"Bhai, aaj BHU campus mein new semester ka first day tha na, full bhaukaal vibes. Subahsubah Central Library ke paas utarte hi lag gaya semester shuru ho gaya hai. Seniors already line mein khade, aankhon mein alag hi chamak. Jaise hi hum log BCA wale ghuse, turant ragda start. Intro do! Arre bhai intro kya, poora biodata maang liya. Ek senior ne toh aise dekha jaise galti se galat department aa gaye ho. Thoda sa kantaap type darr laga, par matargasti bhi chalti rahi. Bhagdad machi jab ek ladka wrong answer bol diya, sab hanshans ke pagal. Uske baad seedha canteen. Vishwanath canteen ki bakaiti toh alag level ki hoti hai. Chai ka glass pakad ke poori duniya discusssemester tough hoga, attendance ka scene, kaunsa teacher kitna strict. Samosa lallantop tha, chutney thodi kam thi par mood chauchak. Wahin pe new classmates se dosti hui. Ek ladki milaayi, same BCA, same hostel, vibe ekdum match. Dusra banda toh itna funny, poori tafri chal rahi table pe. Campus aaj full greengreen, thoda thakaan, thoda excitement. Seniors ka ragda end hotehote thoda chill ho gaya, selfie bhi le li unke saath. Lag raha hai ye semester bhi yaadon se bhara hogaassignments ka rona, canteen ki chai, aur roz ki bakaiti. BHU hai bhai, yahan struggle bhi style mein hota hai."
"Arre yaar, sunn! Kal college fest mein jo gaddar macha hai na, kya bataun tujhe. Matlab pura mahaul ekdum electric tha. Hum log subah se hi full matargasti ke mood mein pahunche the. Main aur Riya jab entry maare, toh crowd dekh ke hi samajh gaye ki aaj scene heavy hone wala hai. Sabse pehle toh humara group dance tha main stage pe. Waise toh rehearsals mein sabne full bakaiti kaati thi, par stage pe chadhte hi energy next level ho gayi. Jaise hi humne finale step mara, public ne jo hooting ki hai... kasam se, performance ekdum chauchak gayi! Apna bhaukaal tight ho gaya tha wahan, sab pooch rahe the ki choreography kisne ki. Lekin asli madness tab shuru hui jab woh celebrity singer aaya. Bhai sahab, stage ke paas aisi bhagdad machi ki puch mat. Log barricade todne ko taiyar the bas ek jhalak dekhne ke liye. Itna dhakkamukki ho raha tha ki hum log chupchap side ho gaye aur canteen nikal liye. Wahan ka paneer roll aur cold coffee ekdum kantaap tha, wahin baith ke humne aadhe ghante dur se logon ki tafri li. Raat mein DJ night pe toh alag hi level ka scene tha. Pura crowd pagla gaya tha, sab ek dusre ke upar gir rahe the par naachna kisi ka band nahi hua. Sach bataun, pair dukh rahe hain aaj, par aisa lallantop fest life mein pehli baar enjoy kiya hai. BCA ka sara coding wala stress nikal gaya ek hi raat mein!"
"Arre yaar, aaj ka din toh mat puch, ekdum panauti tha! Subah se jo baarish shuru hui, mujhe laga normal hai, ruk jayegi. Par Banaras ki sadkon ka haal toh tujhe pata hi hai, aadhe ghante ki baarish mein pura shehar swimming pool ban jaata hai. Main college se nikli hi thi ki Lanka wale road pe itna paani bhar gaya tha ki sadak kahan hai aur gaddha kahan, kuch pata hi nahi chal raha tha. Maine socha side se nikal lun, bas wahin galti ho gayi. Ek auto wale ne achanak se cut maara, aur break lagate hi meri scooty slip ho gayi! Kasam se, pura dress keechad mein san gaya. Wahan chaar log aa gaye help karne, bada bhaukaal ban gaya tha ki Are beti ko chot lag gayi, par mujhe itni sharam aa rahi thi ki mann kiya wahin gayab ho jaun. Uske baad jo traffic mila hai Godowlia taraf, bhai sahab... gadi 1 inch aage nahi badh rahi thi. Log sadak pe hi gadi rok ke bakaiti kar rahe the ki Nagar Nigam so raha hai aur horn bajabaja ke sar dard kar diya. Pura bhagdad wala scene tha, koi idhar bhag raha hai, koi udhar. Jaisetaise bheegte hue 8 baje ghar pahunchi. Mummy gate pe hi khadi thi, chehra dekh ke hi samajh gayi main ki aaj class lagne wali hai. Pehle toh full daant padiPhone kyu nahi kiya? Itni baarish mein matargasti karne ki kya zarurat thi? Kahan ghoom rahi thi? Unko laga main doston ke saath tafri maar rahi thi. Maine jab apni halat dikhayi aur bataya ki gir gayi thi, tab jaake shant hui."
