"Arre sunn! Kal shaam ko hum log Pappu ki adi pe gaye the, wahan ka mahaul dekhne layak tha. Chai ki talab lagi thi, aur wahan ki adrak wali chai toh waise hi kantaap hoti hai. Humne kulhad pakda aur side mein corner pakad liya. Wahan bagal wali bench pe kuch local ladke aur uncles baithe the. Bhai sahab, jo politics pe discussion chal raha tha, lag raha tha parliament yahin shift ho gaya hai. Ek banda full bhaukaal maar raha tha ki Is baar toh bhaiya ji ki hi sarkar banegi, aur dusra uski bakaiti kaat raha tha ki Tumhari analysis zero hai. Itna intense discussion tha ki lag raha tha abhi wahan bhagdad mach jayegi, par Banaras hai, yahan ladai bhi baton se hoti hai. Ek ladka toh alag hi rangbaazi mein tha, bol raha tha vidhayak uska padosi hai. Humne chai ki chuski ke saath unki baatein suni aur doston ke saath full tafri li. Sach bataun, Banaras mein chai ke saath ye muft ka gyan aur entertainment milna lallantop combo hai. Chai khatam ho gayi par wahan se uthne ka mann nahi kar raha tha, time ka pata hi nahi chala unki baatein sunte hue."
"October ka time aate hi Banaras ka mood hi badal jaata hai. Ya toh Durga Puja ka mela, ya Ramleeladono mein same crowd, same excitement. Is baar hum log Ramleela ground gaye. Gate ke paas hi itni bheed thi ki haath chhoot jaaye toh seedha gayab. Lights, music, aur jhanki ka bhaukaal alag level pe. Durga maa ki jhanki dekh ke sach mein goosebumps aa gayeitni detailing, itna glow, ekdum chauchak. Aage badhe toh street food ka attack. Chaat, golgappa, chowmein, aur kulhad wali chaisab ek ke baad ek. Diet ka toh koi scene hi nahi tha. Ek dost bol rahi thi bas ek plate lenge, par teen plate kha ke bhi rukne ka naam nahi. Beechbeech mein selfies, reels, aur random logon se takra ke sorrysorry. Ramleela stage ke paas thodi der ruke. Dialogue suntesunte lag raha tha bachpan wapas aa gaya. Ravan ki entry pe crowd ne itna shout kiya ki kaan baj gaye. Doston ke saath hasimazaak, thodi bakaiti, aur bina baat ke tafri. Pair dard kar rahe the, par mann nahi maan raha tha ghar jaane ko. Raat ko wapas aate time thakaan thi, par dil full. Aise mele sirf festival nahi hote, yaadein ban jaate hain. Banaras ka mela matlab crowd mein bhi apna sa comfort."
"Arre sunn! Kal raat BHU mein jo Garba Night thi na, uska scene ekdum next level tha! Hum log full traditional getup mein taiyar hoke pahunche the. Madhuban ground mein itni bhagdad machi thi entry gate pe ki pucho mat, dhakkamukki karke hum andar ghuse. Par andar ka mahaul dekh ke dil khush ho gaya. Decorations aur lights ekdum chauchak thi. Jaise hi Dholida bajna shuru hua, humne circle banaya aur shuru ho gaye. Mere group ka coordination starting mein thoda hil gaya tha, sab ek dusre ke pair pe dande maar rahe the, full bakaiti chal rahi thi steps ko leke. Par aadhe ghante baad humara flow jo bana hai, bhai sahab, alag hi bhaukaal tight kar diya humne floor pe! Log rukruk ke humara group dance dekh rahe the. Rahul ko dandiya khelna aata nahi, woh bas hawa mein dande ghuma raha tha jaise talwar baazi kar raha ho. Humne uski itni tafri li hai ki woh sharam ke maare side ho gaya. Humne 3 ghante tak nonstop matargasti ki aur pasine se naha gaye. Last mein bhookh itni tez lagi thi ki bahar nikal ke VT (Vishwanath Temple) ke paas cold coffee aur patties dabayi. Woh thandi coffee ekdum kantaap lagi uss time. Pair aaj subah se dukh rahe hain, par kal ki raat ekdum lallantop thi yaar. Agle saal phir machayenge!"
"Kal hostel mein ek chhota sa kaand ho gaya. Friends ke saath milke senior pe prank kiya, aur honestly bolun toh risk bhi tha, par excitement zyada. Woh senior thoda zyada hi serious type ke hainhamesha rules, discipline, ye woh. Toh hum logon ne decide kiya thoda sa fun hona chahiye. Plan simple tha. Unke room ke bahar notice chipka diyaWarden ne urgently bulaya hai, ground floor pe. Ek dost already ground floor pe ready, acting mode on. Jaise hi senior niche aaye, dost ne full confidence ke saath bola, Aapka room inspection mein naam aaya hai. Senior ka face dekhne layak thaekdum tension. Hum log corner mein chup ke khade, hasi control karna mushkil. Phir background se kisi ne mobile pe record chalayawarden ki awaaz jaisi. Tab toh senior aur confuse. Bas 10 second baad hum sab bahar aa gaye, Surprise! Pehle toh gussa aaye, aankh laal, laga ab class lagne wali hai. Par phir khud bhi smile aa gayi unko. Bole, Tum log sudhroge nahi. Uske baad thodi bakaiti hui, chai bhi pilayi unhone. End mein bole prank theek tha, bas zyada mat karna. Us moment pe relief bhi tha aur achievement feel bhi. Friends ke saath aise pranks hi toh college life ko yaadgaar banate hainthoda darr, thodi tafri, aur baad mein full hasi."
"Ramnavami ke din Godaulia ka scene ekdum alag level pe hota hai. Main bhi shaam ko friends ke saath nikal padi. Jaise hi Godaulia ke paas pahunche, lights, music aur crowd dekh ke samajh aa gayaaaj toh bhagdad pakki hai. Road pe jagah hi nahi, har side se log, flags, aur Jai Shri Ram ke chants. Jhanki dekhne ke liye thoda aage ghuse. Ram ji, Sita maa, Lakshman aur Hanuman ji ki jhanki itni sundar thi ki thakaan bhool gaye. Flowers, lights, aur decorations ekdum perfect. Mobile uthaya photo lene, par bheed mein haath hi uparneeche ho raha tha. Ek moment pe dhakka laga, thoda imbalance hua, par dost ne haath pakad liyawarna seedha crowd ke flow mein beh jaati. Itni bheed ke beech bhook bhi lag gayi. Side se chaat wale ki smell aayi toh control nahi hua. Golgappe, aloo tikki, aur last mein kulhad wali chaisab ek ke baad ek. Khaate time bhi log dhakka de rahe the, par maza poora aa raha tha. Godaulia ke mele mein street food ka taste hi alag lagta hai. Wapas aate time pair dukh rahe the, awaaz thak gayi thi, par mann full khush. Ramnavami ka mela sirf jhanki nahi hota, poora Banaras ek saath jeeta hua feel hota hai."
"Arre sunn! Kal raat humne jo senior ke saath bakaiti ki hai na, sunegi toh hasshass ke lotpot ho jayegi. Woh 4th year wale Ravi bhaiya hain na? Jo bada bhaukaal maarte hain ki Main kisi se nahi darta, bhootwuh kuch nahi hota. Kal unka sara darr nikal diya humne. Humne full plan banaya Arts Faculty ke peeche wale raaste pe. Wahan waise hi raat mein sannata rehta hai. Main aur Riya jhadiyon mein chupe the, aur Amit ne hostel se safed bedsheet utha li thi. Jaise hi Ravi bhaiya wahan se phone pe baat karte hue nikle, pehle toh humne ajeebajeeb awaazein nikaali. Woh ruke, idharudhar dekha, thoda dare, par phir matargasti samajh ke aage badhe. Tabhi Amit chadar odh ke Bhoooo karte hue unke samne kood gaya! Bhai sahab, unki jo cheekh nikli hai! Phone haath se chhut gaya aur jo bhagdad machayi hai unhone wahan se... bina peeche dekhe jo bhaage hain, apni chappal tak wahin chhod diye. Hum log wahan girgir ke hase hain, pet dukh gaya hass ke. Unka wo bhaukaali attitude minute mein gayab ho gaya. Baad mein humne VT pe jaake unki chappal wapas ki aur chai peete hue jo tafri li hai unki, ab wo humein dekh ke rasta badal lete hain. Prank ekdum chauchak successful raha, maza aa gaya!"
"BHU ka annual day matlab full excitement aur full tension. Is saal humne dance performance di, aur practice sessions ne toh jaan hi le li. Roz shaam ko class ke baad rehearsalkabhi step match nahi ho raha, kabhi timing gadbad. Dance sir chillate, Energy lao! aur hum paseene mein doobe hote. Beechbeech mein thakaan, thodi bakaiti, aur chai break pe hi jaan aati. Performance wale din stage ke peeche khade the toh dil zorzor se dhadak raha tha. Lights, crowd ki awaaz, aur naam announce hote hi stage fear hit kar gaya. Pair thode numb, haath thande. Ek second ke liye laga ki step bhool jaungi. Phir music start hua, aur jaise body ne khud hi control le liya. Ek step ke baad doosra, phir smile aa gayi. Stage pe aake sab darr nikal gaya. Expressions, moves, formationssab ekdum flow mein. Last pose pe jaise hi music band hua, crowd ka cheer suna. Woh moment bas goosebumps. Taaliyan, whistles, shoutsfull bhaukaal. Stage se utarte hi sab ekdoosre ko hug kar rahe the. Saari practice ki thakaan usi waqt worth lagne lagi. Annual day khatam hua, par yaadein permanent ban gayi. BHU ke stage pe dance karna sirf performance nahi tha, khud pe jeet thi."
"Yaar, aaj life ka ekdum heavy reality check mila mujhe. Main pehli baar himmat karke Manikarnika Ghat gayi thi. Sach bataun, galiyon se guzarte waqt jab Ram Naam Satya Hai ki awaaz aayi, toh dil dhakdhak kar raha tha. Pehle toh pair kaanp rahe the, lag raha tha galti kar di yahan aake. Par jab wahan pahunchi... bhai, wahan ka bhaukaal hi alag hai. Ek taraf chitaayein jal rahi thin, aur dusri taraf life normal chal rahi thi. Shuru mein dimaag mein thodi bhagdad machi ki ye sab kya hai, par thodi der wahan shant khade rehne ke baad ek ajeeb sa sukoon mehsus hua. Hum log roz college mein, sadak pe kitni bakaiti karte hain, chotichoti cheezon pe rote hainki assignment choot gaya ya kisi ne reply nahi kiya. Wahan khade hoke laga ki yeh sab toh bas matargasti hai, asli sach toh yehi hai. Sabko yahin aana hai end mein. Pura ego, sara ghamand mitti mein mil jaata hai. Wahan se wapas aate waqt main ekdum chup thi. Riya bhi saath thi, par humne koi tafri nahi ki, bas chupchap Godowlia tak paidal aaye. Aisa kantaap realization pehle kabhi nahi hua tha. Life kitni unpredictable hai yaar, hum log faltu mein hi stress lete hain. Aaj se no tension, bas khul ke jeena hai. Manikarnika ne bina kuch bole life ka sabse bada lesson sikha diya."
"Oye sunn! Aaj jo BHU ke Amphitheatre ground mein humne aag lagayi hai na, bas puch mat. Pichle do hafte se jo magajmari chal rahi thi practice mein, mujhe toh laga tha pakka popat hoga. Adhe log steps seekhne ke bajaye bakaiti kar rahe the, aur formation banane mein jo bhasad machti thi, sar dard ho gaya tha mera. Aaj jab backstage khade the, toh sach bataun, meri haalat kharab thi. Mann kar raha tha chupchap kalti maar lun wahan se. Aisa lag raha tha sab bhool jaungi. Par jaise hi announcement hua aur hum stage pe gaye... bhai sahab, spotlight padte hi andar ka dar gayab. Music bajte hi humne jo bhaukaal tight kiya hai na, pura crowd pagal ho gaya. Humara coordination ekdum chauchak tha. Woh signature step pe jab public ne shor machaya, toh dil ekdum gardengarden ho gaya. Saamne doston ki toli khadi thi, woh alag hi tafri kaat rahe the aur whistle baja rahe the. Performance ke baad jab sabne bola ki dance kantaap tha, toh saari thakan utar gayi. Exit ke time bheed mein thodi bhagdad mach gayi thi stage ke paas kyunki sabko photo leni thi. Itni matargasti aur mehnat ke baad finally stage pe rock kar diya. Ye din toh lallantop memory ban gaya yaar!"
"Chhath Puja ke time Banaras ka ghar alag hi mode mein chala jaata hai. Subah se hi bhasad machi rehti hai. Mummy orders pe orders de rahi, main aur didi kitchen mein thekua banane mein lage. Aata, gud, gheesab mix kartekarte haath dard kar gaya, par smell itni lallantop thi ki thakaan feel hi nahi hui. Beechbeech mein bakaiti bhi chal rahi thi, kaun sa thekua zyada crispy bana, kaun sa kam. Papa taste tester bane hue the. Nahayekhaye wale din ghar full saafsuthra, ekdum gardengarden feel. Main bhi thoda shaant rehne ka try ki, par honestly magajmari ho jaati hai itne rules follow kartekarte. Phir bhi vibe emotional thi. Shaam ko ghar sajayalights, phool, saare fruits line mein. Dekh ke hi bhaukaal lag raha tha. Arghya wale din toh subah se hi bhagdad. Ghat jaane ki tayyari, saaman sambhalo, dupatta sambhalo. Ghat pe itni crowd ki pair rakhne ki jagah nahi, par sabke chehre pe same belief. Sooraj jaise hi dikha, sabne arghya diya. Us moment pe shor bhi tha, shanti bhi. Dil ekdum bhara hua. Wapas aate time thakaan thi, par mann full sukoon. Friends ka message aaya ghat se, thodi tafri, thodi photos. Chhath Puja sirf ritual nahi hai yahan, poora emotion hai. Banaras mein is time jo feeling hoti hai na, woh kahin aur nahi milti."
"Kal canteen mein jo scene hua na, poora kantaap type. BHU canteen already bheed se bhari thi, upar se bhook aisi ki dimaag kaam hi nahi kar raha. Maine clearly bola, ek masala dosa. Uncle ne haan mein haan milaya, token diya, main friends ke saath bench pe baith ke bakaiti start. 10 minute baad plate aayi aur usmein idli. Plain idli. Do piece. Pehle toh laga shayad kisi aur ka order galti se aa gaya. Phir token dekhamera hi number. Tab toh mood off. Main counter pe gayi aur boli, dosa order ki thi. Uncle full attitude mein, bole, idli bhi toh South Indian hi hai. Ye sunke toh aur gussa aa gaya. Thoda argument hua. Main bol rahi hoon bhai, dosa aur idli same kaise ho gaya. Uncle bol rahe hain ab dosa khatam ho gaya. Peeche line, side se comments, full bhasad. Friends toh maze le rahe, ek ne chupke se video banana start kar diya. Mujhe dekh ke hasi aa rahi thi, par gussa bhi control mein nahi. Finally uncle ne bola, extra chutney de dete hain, idli hi khaa lo. Bhook itni thi ki kalti maarna pada. Idli khayi, taste theek tha, par ego hurt ho chuka tha. Baad mein friends ne video dikhaaya, sab hanshans ke pagal. Reel material mil gaya unko. End mein realize hua, canteen ka galat order bhi college life ka hi part hai. Gussa aata hai, drama hota hai, par baad mein sirf yaadein aur hasi bachti hai."
"Arre yaar, kal raat hostel mein jo kaand hua hai mere saath, sunegi toh has has ke pagal ho jayegi. Main room mein akeli thi, light off karke bas sone hi wali thi. Achanak darwaza dheere se khula... Chuuu ki awaaz aayi. Maine socha hawa hogi. Par tabhi andhere mein ek safed chadar mein lipta hua koi figure dhiredhire meri taraf badhne laga! Kasam se, meri toh saans hi atak gayi. Jai Hanuman Gyan Gun Sagar padhna shuru kar diya maine mann mein. Jaise hi woh figure mere bed ke paas aaya, main itni zor se chillayi ki pura floor hil gaya hoga! Mummyyyy bacha lo! Tabhi achanak light jali aur dekha toh Sneha aur Preeti zameen pe letlet ke hass rahi hain. Un dono ne milke ye bakaiti plan ki thi. Unko lotpot hote dekh mujhe gussa bhi aa raha tha aur hansi bhi. Maine uth ke dono ko takiye se maara. Bada bhaukaal tight kar rakha tha darr ka unhone. Keh rahi thin, Tera chehra dekhne layak tha! Phir humne raat bhar jag ke chai banayi aur purani tafri yaad ki. Aisi matargasti se hi toh hostel life lallantop banti hai, par us time toh jaan hi nikal gayi thi meri!"
"Abey yaar, aaj class mein jo bejjati hua hai na, main kisi ko muh dikhane layak nahi bachi! Verma sir ka lecture chal raha tha C pe, aur tujhe toh pata hi hai woh kitne khadoos hain. Class mein ekdum sannata tha, sui gire toh awaaz aa jaye. Sab log serious hoke notes bana rahe the. Maine galti se phone silent karna bhool gayi thi. Achanak se full volume mein mera phone bajaBaby doll main sone di... Bhai sahab! Woh 10 second meri life ke sabse lambe moments the. Puri class mein jo tafri machi hai! Peeche backbenchers ne toh desk pe haath maarmaar ke hasna shuru kar diya. Sir ne chashma neeche karke mujhe aisi nazar se dekha ki meri rooh kaanp gayi. Unka bhaukaal waise hi tight rehta hai, aaj toh laga mujhe class se seedha suspend karenge. Main sharam ke maare panipani ho gayi. Jaldijaldi bag mein haath daal ke phone dhunda, par bhasad mein mil hi nahi raha tha. Jaisetaise band kiya. Mera chehra laal tamatar ho gaya tha. Lecture khatam hote hi doston ne jo bakaiti ki hai meri, puch mat. Riya bol rahi thi, Wah Guru, kya chauchak background music diya hai tune serious topic pe. Sab mujhe ab Baby Doll bula rahe hain. Kasam se, kal se phone battery nikaal ke hi class mein ghusungi. Aaj toh izzat ka pura raita phail gaya!"
"Ye incident yaad aate hi aaj bhi secondhand embarrassment ho jaata hai. Scene simple thacollege se nikalte time bike pe full style maar rahi thi. Helmet thoda loose, dupatta hawa mein, andar se feeling aa rahi thi ki aaj toh full bhaukaal hai. Aur upar se luck dekho, gate ke paas hi crush khada tha. Nazar padi, confidence aur double. Bas wahi pe popat likha tha. Thoda sa accelerator zyada ho gaya, road pe thodi si ret thi, aur bike phisss seedha balance gaya. Main slow motion mein girti hui, bike side mein, main side mein. Na zyada chot, na kuch, par izzat ka kantaap full lag gaya. Crush seedha bhaag ke aaya, Are you okay? pooch raha. Main uthte hue bol rahi hoon haan haan, sab theek, jaise kuch hua hi nahi. Andar se toh magajmari chal rahi thiye kya ho gaya. Aaspaas log dekh rahe, friends door se hashas ke pagal. Ek boli, style thoda zyada ho gaya. Bike uthayi, dupatta sambhala, aur bina peeche dekhe nikal li. Baad mein friends ne itni bakaiti ki, video bhi circulate. Us din samajh aaya, bhaukaal maarna theek hai, par road aur crushdono ke saamne extra style mehenga pad jaata hai."
"Arre sunn! Aaj jo ghar mein Mahabharat hui hai na, main kya bataun. Maine Mummy ko subah bola tha ki college ki taraf se Industrial Visit hai Sarnath mein, toh shaam tak aungi. Asal mein hum log gaye the Assi pe matargasti karne. Plan ekdum chauchak tha. Humne socha tha ki dopehar mein movie dekh lenge aur phir ghat pe baith ke tafri marenge. Pura din mast nikla, humne pizza khaya, bahut saari photos li, aur full on bakaiti ki. Mujhe laga Mummy ko kya hi pata chalega, main toh apni rangbaazi mein thi. Par meri kismat dekho! Shaam ko jab main ghar ghusi, Mummy sofa pe baithi thin, ekdum shant. Maine jhooth bola, Mummy, factory visit bahut achi thi. Mummy ne bina kuch bole apna phone meri taraf ghuma diya. Bhai, meri saans atak gayi! Mausi ji ne humein Godowlia pe ghumte hue dekh liya tha aur Mummy ko photo bhej di thi. Uske baad jo bhaukaal macha hai ghar mein! Mummy ne jo class lagayi haiTujhe sharam nahi aati? Padhne jati hai ki tafri maarne? Itna bada jhooth bola? Papa bhi aa gaye beech mein, unhone bhi dochaar baatein suna di. Main chupchap gardan jhuka ke khadi thi, lag raha tha ab phone zapt ho jayega. Par phir end mein jab maine bola, Sorry Mummy, agli baar pakka bata ke jaungi, toh Mummy ko bhi thodi hasi aa gayi meri shakal dekh ke. Boli, Chal khana kha le, par agli baar jhooth bola toh taange tod dungi. Bach gayi aaj toh, par thodi der ke liye toh siyappa ho gaya tha!"
"Kal exam hall ka scene yaad karke ab bhi hasi aati hai. Subah se tension full mode mein tha. Stationary ready, notes side pe, mentally bhi poora prep ho gaya tha. Exam hall mein gaye, seat pe baith ke confident feel kar rahi thi ki aaj toh lallantop performance hoga. Paper mila, aur first glance pe hi thoda ajeeb laga. Question paper ka subject mere notes se match nahi kar raha tha. Thodi der check kiya, tab realize huaarre ye toh dusre subject ka paper hai. Pehle toh panic, phir thoda matargasti mode onkya kare, invigilator door hai, shayad samajh na paye. Thoda flip, kuch questions samajhne ki koshish. Par fateh mein na, invigilator ne side se dekha aur seedha meri taraf aaya. Pakad liya. Argh! Full bakaiti class mein. Log hans rahe, kuch friends chilla rahe, Kalti ho gayi, kalti ho gayi! Mein thodi embarrassment aur thodi tension mein, samjha ki ab kaam over. Invigilator ne paper replace kar diya, par mood thoda low ho gaya. End mein paper attempt kiya, par us incident ke baad focus lane mein struggle hua. Class ke friends baarbaar tease kar rahe the, aur ekdum tafri chal rahi thi. Us din samajh aaya, exam mein kalti aur bakaiti dono ek saath aa sakte hain, aur Banaras ka classroom scene full entertainment ka source hai."
"Arre sunn! Kal shaam ko Assi Ghat pe jo comedy hui hai, main batatebatate thak jaungi par teri hasi nahi rukegi. Hum char log stairs pe baithe the, ekdum serious mood mein. Life, career aur breakup pe gehra gyan baant rahe the. Aisa lag raha tha humse bada philosopher koi hai hi nahi Banaras mein. Baatein full flow mein chal rahi thi ki achanak se ek healthy si Gaaye (Cow) aayi aur chupchap hamare circle ke beech mein aa ke baith gayi. Bhai, us time jo bhagdad machi hai wahan! Riya toh Mummyyy chilla ke aise bhaagi jaise bhoot dekh liya ho. Rahul jo bada bhaukaal maar raha tha ki Animals se pyaar karna chahiye, wo sabse pehle kood ke dusri seedhi pe chadh gaya. Hum log itne panic mein the, aur Gai mata ekdum chill baithi thi, jaise wo bhi hamari bakaiti sunne aayi ho. Side wale uncle ne humari photo kheench li uss moment pe. Ab woh photo college ke WhatsApp group mein viral ho gayi hai. Riya ka darra hua chehra dekh ke sab log itni tafri le rahe hain ki pucho mat. Group mein captions aa rahe hainGau Mata giving career advice to BCA students. Izzat ka toh raita phail gaya hai, par kasam se, scene ekdum lallantop tha. Pet dukh gaya hasshass ke!"
"Kal hostel mein jo birthday tha na, poora drama chal gaya. Subah se hi friends full excitement mein, decorations, balloons, aur secret plan bana rahe the. Jab main room mein aayi, ekdum se cake face pe lag gaya. Cream sab over kapde, baal, aur obviously mood full lallantop. Pehle shock, phir hasifriends ke expressions priceless the. Revenge ka plan turant bana. Cake ka thoda hissa aur chocolates leke main unke room mein ghusi. Ekdum matargasti mode on, bas ek throw aur start ho gayi full food fight. Cake, biscuit crumbs, chocolate smearroom ekdum bhasad ho gaya. Log chillate, dodge karte, par maza hi maza. Ek dost toh sofa ke neeche chhup gaya, aur ek corner mein cream ka pit ban gaya. Problem tab hui jab warden ka kadam sunai diya. Sab instantly freeze, aur phir kalti maar ke different corners mein chhup gaye. Warden aayi, dekha, aur bas ek glance maar ke chali gayi. Hum log silently room clean karne lage, par andar se hasi control hi nahi ho rahi thi. Birthday aur revenge dono ek saaththodi tafri, thoda drama, aur full bhaukaal memories. Hostel life ka ye hi charm hai, thoda gussa, thoda bhasad, aur end mein full laughter."
"Oye, aaj Lanka gate pe jo maine bargaining skills dikhayi hain na, tu dekhti toh fan ho jaati meri. Hum log Durga Kund jaane ke liye auto dhoond rahe the. Ek auto wale bhaiya ne humein naya samajh ke seedha 50 rupaye maang liye! Matlab hadd hai bakaiti ki, itni paas ke liye itna paisa? Mera toh dimaag ghum gaya. Maine bhi full attitude mein bol diya, Bhaiya, Banaras mein hi rehte hain, tourist mat samjho humein. Roz ka aanajaana hai, 20 rupaye denge, chalna hai toh chalo. Woh apni magajmari karne laga ki petrol mehenga hai, traffic mein bhasad hai, yeh hai, woh hai. Maine doston ko ishara kiya aur bola, Chalo yaar, dusra dekh lenge. Jaise hi humne wahan se kalti maarne ka drama kiya, peeche se awaaz aayiArre achha baithiye madam, chaliye. Bhai sahab, auto mein baithte waqt jo feeling aayi na, laga jung jeet li hai! 50 se seedha 20 pe laana koi choti baat nahi hai. Meri friends ne auto mein hi taali bajana shuru kar diya, bolinKya bhaukaal tight kiya hai tune, maan gaye guru! Us waqt jo thirty rupaye bachaye, uski khushi kisi jackpot se kam nahi thi. Phir humne unhi bache hue paison se cold drink pi aur pura rasta auto wale ki tafri lete hue gaye. Aaj toh din ekdum lallantop ban gaya bas issi victory se!"
