"Yaar, aaj canteen ka wo kona humari hansi se aise goonj raha tha jaise wahan koi mela laga ho. Hum charomain, Riya, Sneha aur Anshek hi table pe ghus ke baite the aur bakaiti ka level itna high tha ki aaspaas ke juniors humein aise dekh rahe the jaise hum koi ajooba hon. Topic wahi purana tha, ki kaise Sneha ne galti se HOD ko Uncle bol diya tha. Maine uski aisi nakal utari, wahi ghabrahat aur wahi thartharati awaaz, ki Riya ne hansi ke maare apni garam chai table pe phail di. Bechare canteen wale bhaiya baarbaar kapda maarne aa rahe the aur dhere se bol rahe the, Bitiya, thoda dheere, baaki bacche yahan dukh dard baantne aaye hain. Par humein kahan parwah thi? Hum toh apni hi duniya ka bhaukaal jamaye baithe the. Us ek ghante mein humne pure department ki gossips ka falooda banayakaun kisse chupke mil raha hai, kiski back aane wali hai, sab discuss ho gaya. Sach mein, ye jo bina sarpair ki baatein hoti hain na, wahi humein is college ke boring lectures se bachati hain. Jab canteen se nikle toh aisa laga jaise dimaag ka saara stress kalti maar gaya ho. Ye dosti nahi hoti toh shayad college life ek dam sannata hoti."
"Bhai, aaj IT lab mein mere saath jo hadsa hua, usne meri mehnat ka pura satyanaash kar diya. Main pichle do ghante se ek bahut hi complex Python ka code likh rahi thi, jisme 200 se zyada lines thi. Logic ekdum chauchak set kiya tha aur main man hi man khush ho rahi thi ki aaj toh Professor saab meri coding dekh kar dhang se impress ho jayenge. Main apni seat pe full confidence mein baithi thi, doston ko Abhi dikhati hun magic wala look de rahi thi. Jaise hi maine final Run button pe click kiya, mera system wahi freeze ho gaya. Cursor hilna band, screen black, aur mere andar ek ajeeb sa sannata chha gaya. Maine CPU ko doteen baar thapthapaya, dosto se pucha Bhai kya karun?, toh wo apni hi magajmari mein lage the aur bole, Restart kar le, aur koi option nahi hai. Professor paas se guzre, meri phati hui shakal dekhi aur bole, Kya hua bitiya, code darr gaya ya tumhara system tumse gussa hai? Maine jaise hi restart kiya, meri rooh kaanp gayimaine file save hi nahi ki thi! Izzat ka pura falooda ban gaya jab mujhe wapas se Hello World se shuru karna pada. Poori lab mein mere doston ne jo meri tafri li hai, wo dukh main kabhi nahi bhoolungi."
"Aaj ki Economics ki class itni bore thi ki mujhe laga main wahin table pe sar rakh ke so jaungi. Professor saab black hole ki tarah ek hi topic pe lecture diye ja rahe the aur unki awaaz ekdum lori jaisi lag rahi rahi thi. Maine boredom se bachne ke liye apni notebook ka pichla page nikala aur unka ek mast wala cartoon doodle banana shuru kiya. Maine unki wo badi si naak, gusse mein thartharati aankhein aur unke bachekuche dochar baal banane mein itna dhyan lagaya ki mujhe hosh hi nahi raha ki main kahan hun. Main full matargasti mein unke doodle ke bagal mein The Angry Bird likh rahi thi, tabhi class mein ek dum sannata chha gaya. Mujhe laga lecture khatam ho gaya, par jaise hi gardan uthayi, Professor saab mere ekdum piche khade the. Unhone mera chashma dhere se utara aur pucha, Artist banna hai ya economist? Kyunki ye caricature toh mujhse zyada smart lag raha hai. Maine hadbada ke notebook band ki, par tab tak piche baite doston ne dekh liya tha aur sab apna muh dabadaba ke hans rahe celebrities ban gaye the. Class ke baad wo doodle ka photo poore WhatsApp group mein viral ho gaya. Izzat ka aisa falooda hua ki agle char din tak maine class bunk karne ka siyappa hi sahi samjha."
"Project submission ki deadline kal subah hai aur humara group abhi tak department ke corridor mein hi dhera jamaye baitha hai. Suraj dhal gaya, campus ki lights jal gayi, aur pure department mein ek darauna sa sannata hone laga, par humari magajmari thi ki khatam hone ka naam hi nahi le rahi rahi thi. Hum charo ek laptop ke gird aise baithe the jaise koi aag sek rahe hon. Kisi ko pizza khana tha, kisi ko ghar jaake sona tha, aur kisi ko toh bas rona aa raha tha. Hamara leader, Aniket, baarbaar bol raha tha, Bas 5 minute aur, formatting baaki hai, par wo 5 minute kab 2 ghante mein badal gaye, pata hi nahi chala. Laptop ki roshni mein hum sab ke chehre aise thakehare dikh rahe the jaise hum koi jung lad ke aaye hon. Par us thakaan mein bhi jo beechbeech mein bakaiti aur gossips chal rahi thi, usne humein sone nahi diya. Maine jab dekha ki watchman humein ghoorne laga hai, toh humne jaldijaldi sab wrap up kiya. Wo thakaan, wo bhookh, aur department ki un thandi seedhiyon pe baith ke li gayi aakhiri selfie... usme ek alag hi bhaukaal tha. Aisa lagta hai ki ye der raat wali mehnat hi asli college life hai, baaki sab toh bas siyappa hai."
"Bhai, aaj hamare department mein jo bhasad machi thi, wo kisi film ke climax se kam nahi thi. Programming assignment submit karne ki last date thi aur hum mein se kisi ka bhi code run nahi ho raha tha. Tabhi hamara Technical Guru dost, Rahul, messiah banke aaya aur usne group chat pe apni file phenk di. Bas phir kya tha, poore corridor mein ek ajeeb si magajmari shuru ho gayi. Hum 15 log ek hi bench pe laptop khol ke baith gaye aur shuru hua Great Indian CopyPaste ka khel. Koi variable ke naam badal raha tha, toh koi comments delete kar raha tha taaki professor ko shak na ho. Main toh full bhaukaal mein coding change kar rahi thi, par har do minute mein koi piche se chilla raha tha, Oye, line number 45 mein kya likha hai? Sab ekdusre ki shakal dekh rahe the aur darr ke maare sabka bura haal tha. Aakhir mein jab humne submit kiya, toh pata chala sabne galti se Rahul ka Student Name wala comment bhi copy kar liya tha! Izzat ka pura falooda ban gaya jab professor ne sabki file ek saath kholi. Unhone jo lecture pilaya, usse pura department sannata maar gaya. Par sach bataun? Wo jo saath mein milke chori karne ka thrill tha na, usne humari dosti ka bhaukaal aur bada diya. Aaj toh career ka satyanaash hotehote bacha!"
"Yaar, exam ke time hamare college ki library kisi warzone se kam nahi lagti. Aaj subah jaise hi library ka gate khula, hum charo doston ne aisi daud lagayi ki Usain Bolt bhi sharma jaye. Hamein wahi AC ke niche wali corner seat chahiye thi jahan baith ke thodi padhai aur zyada bakaiti ho sake. Main apni heavy bag uthaye seedhiyon pe aisi bhaagi ki meri saans phool gayi, par piche se Riya aur Ansh full speed mein kalti maarne ki koshish kar rahe the. Maine door se hi apna register us table pe phenka taaki meri seat reserve ho jaye, par mera nishana chook gaya aur wo seedha librarian ke table pe ja gira! Bhai, us waqt jo library mein sannata chha gaya, mujhe laga ab toh library card hi cancel ho jayega. Librarian ne aise ghoora jaise main koi terrorist hun. Dosto ne toh wahin hashas ke mera falooda bana diya. Aakhir mein seat toh mil gayi, par pure do ghante hum log wahan padhai kam aur ekdusre ki shakal dekh ke hasne ki matargasti zyada kar rahe the. Library mein khamoshi honi chahiye, par hamare group ka jahan bhi adda jame, wahan siyappa hona toh pakka hai. Aaj ki wo race aur wo beizzati, hamesha yaad rahegi!"
"Aaj ki Analog Communication ki class lene ka mera bilkul mood nahi tha. Dhoop itni tej thi aur professor saab ki awaaz mein itni neend thi ki maine doston ko ishara kiya, Chalo kalti maarte hain! Hum charo dabe paaon piche wale darwaze se nikal gaye, jaise koi jailbreak kar rahe hon. Canteen pahunchte hi jo thandak mili, uff! Humne garam chai aur samoson ka order diya aur shuru hui asli bakaiti. Wahan baith ke humne plan banaya ki kaise agle fest mein bhaukaal machana hai. Par maza tab kirkira hua jab dekha ki hamare wahi professor, jinki class humne bunk ki thi, wo khud dusre table pe baith ke samosa pel rahe the! Hum charo ka wahi satyanaash ho gaya. Humne apna chehra dupatta aur files se chhupane ki koshish ki, par unhone humein dekh liya aur dhere se muskura ke bole, Bitiya, chai achhi hai na? Class mein bhi thodi energy dikhaya karo. Bhai, us waqt jo beizzati feel hui, usne chai ka swaad hi falooda kar diya. Bunk karne ka plan toh mast tha, par kismat ne wahi humara siyappa kar diya. Aaj toh darr ke maare chai bhi gale se niche nahi utar rahi thi."
"Bhai, aaj class mein jo shock laga hai na, usne mere dimaag ka dahi kar diya. Hum log aram se baith ke piche wali bench pe weekend ki matargasti ka plan bana rahe the, tabhi Professor ne achanak bola, Books band karo, surprise quiz hai! Hall mein ekdum sannata chha gaya, jaise kisi ne saari khushiyan cheen li hon. Maine apne doston ki taraf dekha, sabki shakal pe 12 baj rahe the. Mujhe toh ye bhi yaad nahi tha ki hum kaun sa chapter padh rahe hain! Sheet haath mein aate hi mera toh pura satyanaash ho gayaek bhi sawal ka jawab nahi pata tha. Maine dhere se Riya se pucha, Pehle ka answer kya hai?, toh usne ulti sheet dikha di, us bechari ka khud ka falooda ho chuka tha. Maine dimaag lagaya aur har question mein wahi purani ramkatha likh di jo mujhe 10th class se yaad thi. Professor piche se chakkar laga rahe the aur hum sab aisi acting kar rahe the jaise koi bada research paper likh rahe hon. Jab quiz khatam hua, toh canteen mein sabne milke Professor ki burai ki aur dukh manaya. Aaj toh career ka graph ekdum niche girta dikha, par doston ke saath wo blank shakal share karne ka bhi alag hi maza hai."
"Yaar, aaj hamari gang ka sabse bada bakait, Aryan ka birthday tha. Humne plan banaya tha ki canteen mein uska aisa bhaukaal jamayenge ki pura department dekhta reh jayega. Humne chorichupe ek bada sa chocolate cake mangwaya aur canteen ke kone wali table pe dhera jama liya. Jaise hi wo aaya, humne zorzor se gaana shuru kiya, itna shor machaya ki canteen wale bhaiya ko lag raha tha koi protest ho raha hai. Par asli matargasti toh tab shuru hui jab cake kat gaya. Humne use cake khilane ke bajaye uske poore chehre ka falooda bana diya. Uski aankhon se leke uske naye shirt tak, sirf chocolate hi chocolate thi. Wo bechara Bhai chhodo! chillata raha par hum kahan rukne wale the? Sabne mil ke uski aisi birthday bombs waali kutai ki, ki canteen mein baaki bacche hanshans ke pagal ho gaye. Izzat ka toh wahin satyanaash ho gaya tha, par khushi itni thi ki kya bataun. Aakhir mein jab humne canteen saaf karne ka siyappa dekha, toh sab ekek karke kalti maarne lage. Wo bikhra hua cake aur doston ki wo bina matlab ki hansi, sach mein college ki sabse pyaari yaad hai."
"Bhai, aaj subah se pet mein aisi bhagdad machi thi jaise koi exam nahi, jung ka result aane wala ho. Hum sab doston ne himmat jutayi aur department ke notice board ki taraf kadam badhaye. Door se hi wahan logon ka itna bhaukaal tha ki board dikh hi nahi raha tha. Sab ekdusre ke upar chadh ke apna roll number dhoond rahe the. Mera dil aise dhadak raha tha jaise abhi bahar aa jayega. Maine dhere se bheed ko cheera aur jab apni seat number ke aage Pass dekha, toh bhai, aisa laga jaise jannat mil gayi ho! Par asli siyappa tab hua jab maine dekha ki mere best friend ki back lag gayi hai. Wahan jo sannata chha gaya humare beech, wo bahut bhari tha. Maine socha tha thodi bakaiti karenge, party karenge, par uska chehra dekh ke mera apna result ka maza falooda ho gaya. Humne wahan se chupchap kalti maari aur use sambhalne mein lag gaye. Result day hamesha aisi hi khichdi hota haikisi ki lottery lagti hai toh kisi ka satyanaash ho jata hai. Par dosti wahi hai jo Fail hone wale ke saath khadi ho ke kahe, Chal bhai, agle baar phod denge!"
"Aaj college se nikalte hi hum sabka mood ekdum chauchak tha. Hamare college ke paas jo Vishwanath Temple (VT) wala area hai, wahan ke selfie point pe humne aaj full photosession kiya. Maine apni nayi kurti pehni thi aur dosto ne bhi ekdum heroheroine wala look banaya tha. Humne wahan aisiaisi ajeeb shakal wali selfies li ki agar koi stranger dekh leta toh humein pagal hi samajhta. Riya baarbaar phone chheen ke bol rahi thi, Wait, lighting achhi nahi hai!, aur Ansh piche se aake photobomb karke poori pic ka satyanaash kar raha tha. Humne wahan itni matargasti ki, itne pout banaye ki phone ki memory full ho gayi. Log wahan darshan karne aa rahe the aur hum wahan apna alag hi bhaukaal jamaye baithe the. Aakhir mein jab humne wo group photo khichwayi jisme hum sab pagal lag rahe the, tab samajh aaya ki ye selfies hi toh hain jo baad mein yaad aayengi. College life ka ye siyappa kitna bhi thaka de, par doston ke saath ek perfect photo mil jaye toh din ban jata hai. Aaj toh Instagram ke liye content ka pura bhasad mach gaya!"
"Yaar, aaj toh mera din ekdum golden nikal gaya! Lab mein Professor saab sabka logic check kar rahe the aur sabka bura haal thakisi ka loop nahi chal raha tha toh kisi ka syntax error ka siyappa khatam nahi ho raha tha. Main bhi thodi nervous thi, darr lag raha tha ki kahin mera bhi falooda na ban jaye. Jab Sir meri seat pe aaye aur unhone mera code dekha, toh wo 2 minute ke liye ekdum sannata maar gaye. Mujhe laga gaya kaam se, abhi daant padegi! Par unhone palat ke poori class se bola, Dekho, ise kehte hain clean aur efficient logic. Well done! Bhai, us waqt jo mere andar bhaukaal feel hua na, main bata nahi sakti. Mere doston ne piche se Oye topper! bol ke bakaiti shuru kar di. Sir ke jaane ke baad sab mere paas aake bolne lage, Humein bhi sikha de! Maine bhi thoda attitude mein aake bola, Tumhari bas ki baat nahi hai. Itni mehnat ke baad jab koi aapko appreciate karta hai, toh lagta hai ki saari raaton ki magajmari safal ho gayi. Aaj toh khushi ke maare main canteen mein sabko samosa khilane wali hun!"
"aar, aaj toh Economics ki class mein maut ka sannata tha kyunki Professor saab ekek ko khada karke sawal puch rahe the. Sab darr ke maare table ke niche chhupne ki koshish kar rahe the. Tabhi unhone hamare group ke sabse bade gyani dost, Rohan, ko khada kiya. Unhone pucha, What is GDP?, aur Rohan ne itne confidence mein jawab diya ki humein laga ye toh phod dega. Usne bola, Sir, GDP matlab Ghar ka Domestic Paisa! Bhai, us ek second ke baad jo class mein hansi ka dhamaka hua na, professor saab ka gussa bhi wahi kalti maar gaya. Hum log bench thapthapa ke has rahe the aur Rohan bechara aise khada tha jaise usne koi Nobel Prize wala logic diya ho. Uska confidence ekdum chauchak tha par answer ekdum falooda. Professor ne bhi muskura ke bola, Beta, itni nayi economy mat banao. Class ke baad humne uska itna satyanaash kiya, itni bakaiti ki, ki wo bechara canteen se bhaag gaya. Aaj toh beizzati ka level ekdum top pe tha, par maza bahut aaya!"
"Bhai, aaj department ne ek Career Guidance seminar rakha tha aur attendance mandatory kar di thi. Hum sab bade banthan ke seminar hall mein baithe ki shayad kuch bhaukaal seekhne ko milega. Par jaise hi speaker ne bolna shuru kiya, humein samajh aa gaya ki ye toh neend ki goli hai. Wo banda 1990 ki baatein kar raha tha aur uska tone itna flat tha ki hall mein aadhe log toh bina pillow ke hi so gaye. Main aur Riya piche baith ke apna alag hi siyappa chala rahe the. Humne speaker ke har boring sentence pe memes banana shuru kiya. Tabhi speaker ne pucha, Any questions?, aur mere dost ne neend mein chillaya, Sir, lunch kab hai? Bhai, wahan jo sannata chha gaya, professor ne humein aisi nazron se dekha ki laga abhi suspension letter mil jayega. Seminar se bahar nikalte hi humne aisi matargasti kari jaise jail se chhute hon. Do ghante ki wo magajmari ne humara dimaag ekdum khaali kar diya tha. Aisa seminar dobara hua toh main pakka kalti maar lungi!"
"Yaar, college fest aane wala hai aur hamari gang mein abhi se bhaukaal macha hua hai. Aaj hum canteen mein baith ke pura Master Plan bana rahe the. Maine bola ki hum log dance competition mein part lenge, toh Aniket ne bola, Pehle chalna toh seekh le! Wahi se shuru hui hamari bakaiti. Humne decide kiya ki hum sab ek hi color ke kapde pehnenge taaki department mein hamara alag hi rob dikhe. Hum log budget discuss kar rahe the par baat ghumfir ke wahi aa gayi ki ladkiyonladkon ko impress kaise karna hai. Maine plan diya ki hum ek stall lagayenge, par fund ke naam pe humare paas sirf 50 rupaye the. Pura plan ekdum chauchak tha par implementation ka satyanaash hona pakka lag raha tha. Phir bhi, wo jo excitement hoti hai na fest ki, wo doston ke saath milke double ho jati hai. Humne decide kiya ki kuch ho na ho, halla itna machayenge ki poore college mein humara hi siyappa chhaya rahe. Fest ka toh pata nahi, par hamari planning mein hi poora din matargasti mein nikal gaya."
"Bhai, aaj Physics lab mein mere saath jo kaand hua, main kabhi nahi bhoolungi. Hum log Electric Circuit wala experiment kar rahe the. Maine full bhaukaal mein taarein (wires) idharudhar jodi aur switch on kiya. Maine socha tha ki bulb jalega aur meri wahwahi hogi, par bulb jalne ke bajaye ek chhota sa patakha phuta aur poore lab mein dhuen ka satyanaash ho gaya. Professor saab daurte huye aaye aur unhone jo mujhe sunaya, mera pura confidence wahi kalti maar gaya. Bitiya, scientist banna hai ya terrorist?, unhone chillake pucha. Mere doston ne toh door khade hoke meri aisi tafri li, ki mera chehra sharam se laal ho gaya. Maine saara circuit ulta laga diya tha! Izzat ka pura falooda ban gaya jab mujhe wapas se report file likhne ko kaha gaya. Aaj toh lab mein mera jo siyappa hua hai, usne mujhe ye samjha diya ki coding hi theek hai, ye bijli ke jhatke mere bas ki baat nahi. Pura din bas daant khane mein hi nikal gaya!"
"Yaar, aaj mess ka khana dekh kar hi mera mood ekdum satyanaash ho gaya tha, toh maine doston se bola, Chalo canteen, aaj kuch chauchak khate hain! Hum sabne wahan ka mashoor Masala Dosa order kiya. Bhai, jaise hi wo plate saamne aayi, uski khushboo se hi dil gardengarden ho gaya. Dosa itna bada aur itna crispy tha ki table pe jagah hi kam pad gayi. Pehli byte lete hi aisa laga jaise jannat mil gayi hosambar ka wo teekhakhatta swaad ekdum kantaap tha! Hum charo doston mein dosa chheenne ki aisi bhasad machi ki canteen wale bhaiya bhi hansne lage. Main aur Riya toh chutney ke peeche hi pad gaye. Wo jo canteen ki dhoop mein baith ke, bina kisi tension ke thanda coke aur garam dosa pelne ka maza hai na, wo kisi 5star hotel mein nahi mil sakta. Humne wahan baith ke itni matargasti kari ki doosre bacche humein ghoorne lage. Aaj toh pet aur man dono ekdum tript ho gaye, sach mein wo dosa hamare poore din ka highlight ban gaya!"
"Bhai, aaj mera presentation tha aur maine poori raat jaag ke slides banayi thi. Maine socha tha ki stage pe jaake ekdum bhaukaal macha dungi, par jaise hi Professor ne mera naam pukara, mere pairon tale zameen khisak gayi. Jab main stage pe khadi hui aur saamne 60 logon ki aankhein mujhpe tiki dekhi, toh mere dimaag mein ekdum sannata chha gaya. Mera gala sookh gaya aur jo words maine ratti thi, wo sab dimaag se kalti maar gaye. Maine dhere se bolna shuru kiya, Good morning everyone, today my topic is... aur tabhi meri awaaz phat gayi. Piche se mere doston ne thoda sa halla machaya taaki main relax ho jaun, par meri ghabrahat ka siyappa aur badh gaya. Maine pointer ulta pakad liya aur slides aagepiche hone lagi. Izzat ka pura falooda bante dikh raha tha. Par phir maine ek gehri saans li aur bas bolti chali gayi. Jab khatam hua aur sabne taaliyan bajayi, tab jaake meri saans mein saans aayi. Presentation toh theekthaak nikal gayi, par wo jo shuruwat ka darr tha, usne mera pura satyanaash kar diya tha. Aaj pata chala ki public speaking kitni badi magajmari hai!"
"Yaar, aaj doston ke beech baithna mere liye thoda bhari pad gaya. Hum log canteen mein baite the aur main bade maze se ek samosa utha rahi thi, tabhi Ansh ne meri taraf dekh ke bola, Oye, thoda kam kha, varna agle semester tak department ke darwaze se nikalna mushkil ho jayega! Bhai, usne itne zor se bola ki aaspaas ke log bhi hansne lage. Phir kya tha, poori gang shuru ho gayi meri bakaiti karne. Riya ne toh hadh hi kar di, boli Iska face ab ekdum golgappa jaisa lagne laga hai. Maine unhe ghoor ke dekha aur bola Main khaatepeete ghar ki hun!, par andar hi andar mujhe thoda bura lag raha tha. Izzat ka pura falooda ban chuka tha. Unhone mujhe chubby aur motu bolbol ke itna chidhaaya ki maine wo samosa wapas plate mein rakh diya. Ye dosti mein jo bina matlab ki tafri hoti hai na, kabhikabhi dil ko chubh jati hai. Maine gusse mein wahan se kalti maarne ki koshish ki, par phir unhone aake Sorry bola aur bola ki main jaisi hun ekdum chauchak hun. Doston ka yahi toh siyappa haipehle mazaak udayenge aur phir emotional karke mana lenge."
"Aaj hamare department ka corridor kisi news channel se kam nahi lag raha tha. Har kone mein doteen log khusarpusar kar rahe the, aur maine aur meri gang ne bhi socha ki thodi magajmari kar hi lete hain. Pata chala ki hamari department ki sabse strict maam aur sabse khadoos sir ke beech kuch chakar chal raha hai! Bhai, ye sunte hi humare beech aisi bhagdad machi ki hum sab ek jaisa logic lagane lage. Hum corridor mein khade hoke aisi bakaiti pel rahe the ki kaun kiske saath kahan dekha gaya. Har guzarte huye professor ko hum aise dekh rahe the jaise hum koi detective hon. Corridor ka wo sannata aaj fullon gossips se bhara hua tha. Maine bola, Abhi dekhna, agle internal marks mein sabka satyanaash hone wala hai. Beechbeech mein seniors bhi aake apni information de rahe the. Aaj padhai toh ek taraf reh gayi, bas ye gossip ka bhaukaal hi chalta raha. Aakhir mein jab HOD nikle aur unhone humein wahan se bhagaya, tab jaake ye siyappa khatam hua. College mein padhai se zyada maza toh in masaledar baaton mein hi aata hai!"
"Yaar, aaj subah se hi dimaag ka siyappa ho rakha tha kyunki pehla lecture hi sabse boring professor ka tha. Hum sab darrdarr ke class mein ghuse, par jaise hi dekha ki podium khaali hai, poori class mein ekdum chauchak jashn ka mahaul ban gaya! Pata chala professor saab aaj absent hain. Bas phir kya tha, class hall nahi, balki koi machhli bazaar ban gaya. Hum piche wali bench pe baith ke aisi bakaiti karne lage ki monitor ki bhi himmat nahi hui humein chup karane ki. Koi bench thapthapa raha tha, toh koi phone pe gaane baja raha tha. Hum charo doston ne toh wahan Antakshari shuru kar di aur har doosre gaane pe kisi na kisi professor ki nakal utarna shuru kar diya. Izzat ka toh wahin falooda ban raha tha, par humein kahan parwah thi? Poori class mein ek ajeeb si bhagdad machi hui thikoi paper ke jahaj uda raha tha toh koi canteen jaane ki planning kar raha tha. Wo ek ghante ki matargasti ne poore din ki thakaan kalti maar di. Jab HOD piche se guzre aur unhone wo shor suna, tab jaake sab darr ke maare aise baith gaye jaise koi bahut bada research paper padh rahe hon. Wo moments hi toh asli college life hain!"
"Bhai, aaj ki dhup itni pyaari thi ki hamara mann department ke band kamron mein bilkul nahi laga. Hum sab doston ne apna bag uthaya aur seedha college ground ke us purane ped ke niche dhera jama liya. Wo hamara permanent adda hai, jahan baith ke humne duniya bhar ki magajmari kari hai. Aaj wahan baith ke humne future, career aur dosti pe aisi deep baatein ki, jo class mein kabhi nahi ho paatin. Ground pe chal rahe cricket match ko dekhna aur beechbeech mein ball aane pe Oye, humein mat maarna! chilanaalag hi maza tha. Maine apna lunch box khola aur wahan jo chheenjhapat shuru hui, usne meri rotiyon ka satyanaash kar diya, par doston ki hansi ne sab recover kar liya. Wahan ka sannata aur ped ki chhaon mein doston ke saath wo purani yaadon ka bhaukaal... uff! Aisa lag raha tha ki waqt yahin ruk jaye. Ground pe baith ke humne jitne sapne dekhe hain, utne shayad library mein bhi nahi dekhe honge. 22 saal ki umar mein ye dosti hi hamara sabse bada bhaukaal hai, aur ye adda hamari safe jagah."
"aar, exam sar pe hain aur meri notebooks ka haalat aisi hai jaise kisi ne unpe satyanaash kar diya hoaadhe pages khaali aur aadhe pe doodles! Maine hadbada ke apni Topper dost, Priya, ko phone milaya aur bola, Behen, tere notes de de, varna mera result falooda ban jayega. Hum department ke piche wali bench pe mile. Jab usne apni neetandclean notebook dikhayi, toh mujhe apni shakal pe sharam aane lagi. Wahan baith ke humne notes exchange kiye, par notes lene se zyada wahan bakaiti shuru ho gayi. Maine use bataya ki kaise main poore semester bas matargasti karti rahi aur ab darr lag raha hai. Wo mujhe samjha rahi thi aur main uske notes mein se diagram copy karne ki koshish kar rahi thi. Beech mein ek aur dost aa gaya aur usne shuru kar diya Oye, mujhe bhi share kar do! Phir kya tha, notes sharing ka pura siyappa ek group study mein badal gaya. Baithne gaye the 10 minute ke liye, par 2 ghante kab nikal gaye, pata hi nahi chala. Notes toh mil gaye, par unhe padhne ki himmat abhi bhi kalti maari hui hai!"
"Bhai, aaj Annual Function ki pehli dance practice thi aur maine full excitement mein apna naam de diya tha. Hum auditorium mein jama huye aur hamara senior, jo choreographer bana tha, usne full bhaukaal mein music bajaya. Maine socha tha ki Bollywood heroine ki tarah thumke lagaungi, par jaise hi beat shuru hui, mere pairon ka siyappa shuru ho gaya. Main right ja rahi thi toh baaki sab left! Oye, bitiya! Dance karna hai, kusti nahi, choreographer ne chillake bola aur poore group mein hansi ka dhamaka hua. Izzat ka wahin falooda ban gaya. Maine phir se try kiya, par is baar main phisal ke seedha monitor ke upar giri. Mere doston ne piche se Waah, kya step hai! bol ke aisi tafri li ki mera chehra laal ho gaya. Practice mein p  behne ke bajaye sirf beizzati beh rahi thi. Par sach bataun, wo bikhre huye steps aur doston ke saath wo dhakkemukki waali practice mein jo maza tha, wo performance mein bhi nahi hoga. Aaj toh poora din dance ke chakkar mein thak ke satyanaash ho gaya hai, par dimaag mein abhi bhi wahi gaana goonj raha hai!"
"Yaar, kal semester exam hai aur aaj hamare poore group ki halat aisi hai jaise koi ICU ke bahar baitha ho. Hum sab ne department ke khaali classroom mein dhera jama liya, tablekursi ek saath lagayi aur shuru hui Last Minute Magajmari. Har table pe ek alag hi bhasad machi thikisi ko basic logic nahi pata tha toh koi 5th unit ke dukh mein ro raha tha. Maine socha thoda leadership dikhati hun, toh maine board pe bada sa diagram banaya, par do minute mein hi mujhe samajh aa gaya ki maine khud hi sab galat likha hai. Izzat ka wahin falooda ban gaya jab Riya ne pucha, Behen, ye circuit hai ya spaghetti? Phir kya tha, padhai kam aur ekdusre ki shakal dekh ke hasne ki bakaiti zyada shuru ho gayi. Humne ekdusre ko daraaya, Bhai agar ye question aa gaya toh sabka satyanaash pakka hai! Raat hone ko aayi, canteen se thandi chai aur biscuits aaye, aur us thakaan mein jo doston ka saath mila, wahi asli sukoon tha. Pata nahi kal exam mein kya hoga, par aaj ki wo group study wali matargasti ne darr ko thodi der ke liye kalti maarne pe majboor kar diya."
"Bhai, aaj meri kismat ne mere saath wo siyappa kiya hai ki main kisi ko muh dikhane layak nahi bachi. Main full attitude mein, nayi safed kurti pehen ke canteen mein entry maari thi, haath mein cold coffee ka glass liye. Socha tha thoda cool vibe dungi. Tabhi hamara sabse bada nautanki dost, Ansh, piche se Bhoot! chillate huye aaya aur usne mujhe jhatka de diya. Agle hi second, meri cold coffee hawa mein lehrayi aur dharam se meri kurti ke upar! Yaar, us waqt jo canteen mein sannata chha gaya, aur phir jo sabke hasne ka bhaukaal shuru hua, mera mann kiya main wahin zameen mein dhans jaun. Safed kurti pe brown coffee ka nishaan aisa lag raha tha jaise kisi ne naksha bana diya ho. Izzat ka pura falooda ban gaya jab sabne chidhana shuru kiya, Oye, coffee pee rahi thi ya naha rahi thi? Maine washroom jaake saaf karne ki koshish ki, par nishaan aur bada ho gaya. Poora din mujhe dupatta aise lapet ke ghumna pada jaise main koi chori karke bhaag rahi hun. Aaj toh meri style ka ek dum satyanaash ho gaya!"
"Aaj lecture bunk karne ke baad hum sab chupke se department ki rooftop pe nikal gaye. Wahan ka mausam itna chauchak tha aur itni thandi hawa chal rahi thi ki saari boring classes ka dukh kalti maar gaya. Hum wahan ki deewar pe line se baith gaye, pair latka ke, aur poore campus ko upar se dekh rahe the. Wahan jo shanti thi na, wo library mein bhi nahi milti. Humne wahan baith ke aisiaisi bakaiti kari, purane doston ke kisse sunaye aur aane wale career ko leke thodi magajmari bhi ki. Riya ne apna bluetooth speaker nikala aur dhere se gaane baja diye. Aisa lag raha tha jaise hum kisi film ke scene mein hain, jahan sab kuch ekdum perfect hai. Niche se professors ke guzarne ki awaaz aa rahi thi aur hum upar baith ke unki shakal dekh ke dhere se hans rahe the. Wo rooftop hamari secret jagah ban gayi hai jahan college ka saara stress khatam ho jata hai. Aaj wahan baith ke jo sukoon mila, usne dil ekdum gardengarden kar diya. Sach mein, doston ke saath aisi matargasti hi life ka asli bhaukaal hai."
"Bhai, har baar guest lecture neend ki goli hota hai, par aaj ka scene ekdum alag tha. Ek young entrepreneur aaye the Startups pe baat karne. Unka bolne ka andaaz itna chauchak tha ki poore hall mein maut ka sannata nahi, balki excitement ka bhaukaal tha. Main jo pehle bench pe baith ke sone ka plan bana rahi thi, unki baatein sunke ekdum alert ho gayi. Unhone bataya ki kaise 22 saal ki umar mein hum apna khud ka kuch shuru kar sakte hain. Maine pehli baar kisi lecture mein notes lene ki magajmari kari aur stage pe jaake ek sawal bhi pucha. Mere doston ne piche se Oye scientist! bol ke thodi bakaiti karne ki koshish ki, par main aaj full serious mode mein thi. Lecture ke baad hum sab doston ne canteen mein baith ke apna khud ka startup idea discuss kiya, bhale hi hamare paas investment ke naam pe sirf 100 rupaye the. Aaj pehli baar laga ki college sirf degrees ke liye nahi, balki dimaag kholne ke liye bhi hai. Wo lecture ne mere future ke darr ka satyanaash kar diya aur mujhe ek nayi energy de di. Aaj ka din sach mein bahut fruitful raha!"
"Yaar, aaj toh meri kismat ne mera wo satyanaash karaya ki kya bataun. Digital Electronics ki class chal rahi thi aur Professor saab ekdum maut ka sannata banakar lecture le rahe the. Maine apna phone bag mein rakha tha, par galti se Silent ke bajaye Vibrate pe reh gaya. Tabhi hamare group ki sabse badi bakait, Sneha, ka call aa gaya. Wood ke table pe rakha mera bag BrrrBrrr karke aise kaampne laga jaise wahan earthquake aa gaya ho. Poori class ki nazar mere bag pe thi. Professor ne lecture roka aur dhere se mere paas aake bole, Bitiya, lagta hai tumhare bag mein koi bhoot ghus gaya hai, ya phir tumhare doston ki magajmari shuru ho gayi hai? Bhai, us waqt jo meri beizzati ka falooda bana na, main bata nahi sakti. Unhone mera phone zabt (seize) kar liya aur mujhe poori class ke saamne khada rakha. Mere dost piche baith ke dheredhere hans rahe the aur main wahan Error 404 wala muh leke khadi thi. Aaj toh meri Sincere Student wali image ka pura siyappa ho gaya!"
"Bhai, aaj semester ka aakhiri din tha, toh hum sabne decide kiya ki college gate ke saamne ek aisi photo khichwayenge jo ekdum bhaukaal lage. Hum sabne apna best outfit pehna tha aur gate ke College Name ke niche line se khade ho gaye. Maine socha tha ki ekdum Student of the Year wali vibe aayegi. Humne guard bhaiya ko request karke camera pakdaya aur bola, Bhaiya, ekdum chauchak photo lena. Par kismat ka khel dekho, jaise hi unhone click kiya, ek awara kutta hamare frame mein ghus gaya aur Ansh ne darr ke maare aisi shakal banayi jaise usne koi bhoot dekh liya ho. Jab humne photo dekhi, toh hum sab ekdusre ka chehra dekh ke hashas ke pagal ho gaye. Izzat ka toh wahi satyanaash ho gaya tha, par wo photo hamare poore group ka sabse bada meme ban gayi. Humne wahan khade hoke kam se kam 50 photos khichi, kabhi serious toh kabhi full matargasti wali. Aaj us gate se nikalte waqt thoda dukh toh tha, par doston ke saath wo photosession ne mood ekdum gardengarden kar diya."
"Bhai, aaj jo tension hui hai na, usse mera blood pressure uparneeche ho gaya. Project submission mein sirf 15 minute baki the aur hum log department ke paas wali dukan pe print nikalne gaye. Jaise hi meri baari aayi aur maine pendrive lagayi, printer ne ajeeb si karrkarr awaaz kari aur wahi dum tod diya. Dukan wale bhaiya bole, Bitiya, ink khatam ho gayi aur paper phas gaya hai. Mere dimaag mein ekdum sannata chha gaya! Main wahan rone wali ho gayi thi kyunki agar submit nahi hota toh internal marks ka satyanaash hona pakka tha. Mere doston ne wahan aisi bhasad machai, koi paper nikal raha tha toh koi dusri dukan dhoondne ke liye bhaag raha tha. Aakhir mein humne dusre block ke printer se print nikalwaya aur main corridor mein aise bhaagi jaise koi Olympic race ho. Jab 1 minute pehle file submit kari, tab jaake jaan mein jaan aayi. Aaj toh technology ne mera pura falooda bana hi diya tha, par doston ki magajmari ne bacha liya."
"Yaar, college fest aane wala hai aur hamara department ekdum dulhan ki tarah saj raha hai. Aaj main aur meri gang poore din department ki floor pe baith ke badebade charts aur posters bana rahe the. Maine socha tha ki main ekdum artist ki tarah chauchak poster banaungi, par paint brush uthate hi mera pura hath aur kurti neelapeela ho gaya. Hum sabne milke wahan itni bakaiti kari ki poster kam aur Holi zyada lag rahi thi. Riya ne galti se glue ki bottle ulat di aur mera hath chart paper se chipak gaya! Bhai, us waqt jo siyappa hua, sabne milke mujhe churaya aur mera poster toh wahi phat gaya. Par humne haar nahi maani, humne un phate huye pieces se hi ek Abstract Art wala poster bana diya aur HOD ko bola ki ye New Age Design hai. Unhone bhi haske Theek hai bol diya. Aaj poore din paint mein lathpath hoke, doston ke saath wo matargasti karke aisa laga ki college sirf padhai ke liye nahi, balki inhi yaadon ke liye hai. Izzat ka falooda toh roz hota hai, par ye maza roz nahi milta!"
"Yaar, aaj toh dimaag ka pura dahi ho gaya. Saturday tha, mausam ekdum chauchak ho rakha tha aur hum sabne plan banaya tha ki 1 baje nikal ke nayi movie dekhne jayenge. Sabne apna bag pack kar liya tha, doston ke beech movie ke spoilers ki bakaiti shuru ho gayi thi, tabhi Professor Sharma ne entry maari aur bade pyaar se bole, Bacchon, syllabus piche hai, toh aaj hum 2 ghante ki extra class lenge. Bhai, us waqt class mein jo sannata chha gaya na, aisa laga jaise kisi ne jeeti hui lottery chheen li ho. Hum sab ekdusre ki shakal dekh rahe the aur man hi man Professor ka satyanaash kar rahe the. Maine Riya ki taraf dekha, wo toh rone wali ho gayi thi. Poore do ghante hum wahan murdon ki tarah baithe rahe, dimaag mein lecture nahi balki popcorn aur samosa chal raha tha. Professor saab full energy mein black hole samjha rahe the aur humein apna future black hole mein dikh raha tha. Aaj toh hamare weekend plan ka pura falooda ban gaya. Jab class se nikle, toh movie ka show chhoot chuka tha aur hum sab bas canteen mein thandi chai pi ke apna dukh kalti maarne ki koshish kar rahe the."
