"Yaar, finals khatam hone wale hain aur department ke corridor mein ab padhai se zyada AfterParty ka bhaukaal hai. Aaj hum sab department ki balcony mein khade hoke plan bana rahe the ki kahan jaana hai. Koi keh raha tha Rooftop Cafe, toh koi keh raha tha Water Park. Maine bola, Bhai, pehle ye toh dekh lo ki kiske paas kitne paise bache hain!, aur wahi hamari party ka satyanaash hona shuru ho gaya. Hum sabne apni pocket money calculate ki toh pata chala hum sirf ek plate momos aur ek thandi cold drink hi afford kar sakte hain. Par doston ka jo siyappa hota hai na, wo budget ka mohtaj nahi hota. Humne decide kiya ki hum sab milke kisi ke ghar pe Potluck party karengekoi maggi layega, koi chips, aur koi sirf apni bakaiti lekar aayega. Humne wahan khade hoke jo sapne bune, jo purani yaadon ka falooda banaya, usse dil ekdum gardengarden ho gaya. Semester kaisa bhi gaya ho, par doston ke saath ye aakhiri jashn ka plan hi humein zinda rakhta hai. Ab bas ye exams kalti maarein, phir toh humara hi raaj hoga!"
"Bhai, aaj subahsubah kismat ne aisi kalti maari ki kya bataun. Main thoda late ho gayi thi aur upar se mera ID card hostel ke room mein hi chhoot gaya tha. Maine socha thoda smile deke aur Bhaiya, please bolke nikal jaungi, par aaj gate pe wahi sabse khadoos wale guard uncle khade the. Unhone mera rasta aise roka jaise main koi border cross kar rahi hun. Maine full bhaukaal mein bola, Uncle, main Final Year ki student hun, shakal se nahi lagta kya? Unhone thandak se jawab diya, Bitiya, shakal pe ID card nahi chipka hota. Izzat ka wahin falooda ban gaya! Mere dost gate ke andar khade hoke meri tafri le rahe the aur video bana rahe the. Maine unhe ishara kiya ki help karo, toh wo piche se chilla rahe hain, Hum ise nahi pehchante, ye koi outsider hai! Bhai, us waqt jo sannata mere dimaag mein chhaya na, man kiya wahi dharti phat jaye. Aakhir mein jab Riya ne apni bag se mera purana library card dikhaya, tab jaake entry mili. Aaj toh meri dignity ka pura satyanaash ho gaya gate pe hi!"
"Aaj se placement season start hone wala hai aur dimag ekdum chipak gaya tension mein. Subahsubah se lag raha, Kya hoga? Kaunse companies aayenge? Resume sahi hai ya nahi? Interview kaise denge? Har chhoti cheez pe magajmari chal rahi hai. Friends full preparation mode mein, aur main bas thoda nervous, thoda anxious feel kar rahi hoon. Office wear ka plan, resume check, aptitude questionssab mind mein repeat ho raha hai. Kabhi lagta hai ready hoon, kabhi lagta hai poora nervous aur kalti type ho gaya. Ghar pe bhi papamummy bas silent mode, shayad unka confidence dikh raha hai, par andar ka darr clear hai. Raat ko thodi der Ganga ke paas baith ke practice ki aur breathe li. Hawa thodi calm, aur paani ka flow dekh ke thoda relax feel hua. Lekin andar ka tension still chipka haiplacement season ka bhaukaal aur expectations dono ek saath aa gaye hain. Kal se shuru ho jaayega poora processinterview, group discussion, aur test. Abhi sirf darr hai, par thoda preparation aur tafri plan ke saath manage ho jaayega. Banaras ke is student life ka ye hi level haiek taraf stress, ek taraf full hope aur excitement ka combo."
"Aaj ka din thoda low feel ho raha hai. Internship ke liye apply kiya tha, aur ab tak reply nahi aaya. Pehle laga shayad busy honge, par dheeredheere wait karte karte tension chipak gaya. Har phone check, har mail checkkabhi notification, kabhi disappointment. Dimag mein full magajmari chal rahi haiKya resume sahi tha? Cover letter okay tha? Ya fir competition zyada hai? Friends ke messages aa rahe, sab bol rahe Thoda wait kar, reply aayega, par andar ka gardengarden feeling khali sa lag raha hai. Kabhi lagta hai kalti ho gayi, kabhi lagta hai next week aayega reply. Raat ko thodi der Ganga ke paas baith ke socha, paani ka slow flow aur hawa ka thoda calm feel, bas tension ko halka kar diya. Samajh aaya, patience aur plan dono chahiye. Reply na aana matlab failure nahi hai, sirf timing ka issue hai. Kal phir resume check karungi, followup karungi, aur ekdo aur applications bhi bhej dungi. Abhi bas thoda disappointment, thoda wait, aur thoda planning chal rahi hai. Banaras ka student life ka ye hi bhaukaalek taraf tafri, ek taraf expectations, aur har step pe thodi bakaiti aur bhasad bhi."
"Bhai, aajkal meri life full confusion mode mein hai. Internship ke liye resume banana start kiya, aur lagta hai poora brain ka fuse ud gaya. Pehle socha ek page mein simple sa lallantop resume banau, par jaise hi Word open kiya, bhagdad machi. Fonts, colors, sectionssab kuch confusing lag raha tha. Ek hi line pe 10 minute debate chal gaya ki ye line important hai ya bakaiti hai. Skills ka section toh aur bhi bhasad tha. Matlab, Python mention karun ya sirf basics likhun? Projects kaunsa highlight karun? Group project ka detail daalu ya simple mention kar du? Ek taraf toh matargasti chal rahi thi ki impress karna hai, dusri taraf stress ki level full kantaap. Friends ne bhi suggest kiyaThoda modern style daal, LinkedIn link bhi de de, par mera style thoda chauchak hai, traditional sa. Template bhi select kartekarte ek ghanta nikal gaya. Ek template full fancy tha, par lag raha tha ki HR ko read karte karte headache ho jaayega. Dusra simple, par lag raha tha boring ho jayega. Laptop ke saamne baithi baithi, main poora tafri mode mein thichai leke aayi, music on kiya, fir bhi focus zero. End mein decide kiya, ek compromiseekdum professional look, thoda personal touch, aur projects aur skills ka best mix. Save kar ke dekha, ekdum lallantop lag raha tha. Feeling aayi, haan yaar, kuch toh toh ready ho gaya. Resume banwana simple kaam nahi hai bhai, poora bhaukaal aur confusion ka combo hai."
"Bhai, kal raat ka scene yaad aate hi full tension mode yaad aa jaata hai. Coding practice mein phasa hua tha aur dimaag bilkul chipak gaya. Subah se college aur assignments ke stress ke baad, raat ko laptop ke saamne baith ke poora code likhne ki koshish kar rahi thi. Ek function nahi chal raha tha, error ka message baarbaar aa raha thafull bhaukaal tension. Pehle try kiya, debug kiya, fir stackoverflow pe search kiya, magajmari chalti rahi. Ek point pe laga jaise laptop ka screen aur mera dimag dono hi bandh ho gaye ho. Chai leke aayi, par kuch kaam nahi aaya, aankhen laal ho gayi, aur haath bhi thak gaye. Friends ne WhatsApp pe memes bheje, par mood bilkul kaam ka nahi lag raha tha. Raat bhar matargasti aur frustration ke beech code ko samajhne ki koshish. Kabhi lagta, Kalti ho gayi, kalti ho gayi, kabhi lagta Bas ek aur try aur, ho jaayega. Laptop ke light mein, room mein silence, aur sirf keyboard ki awaazfull coding ka drama chal raha tha. Finally, 3 baje ke aaspaas ek function chal gaya aur relief ka level alag hi tha. Heartbeat slow, smile chhoti si, aur lag raha tha jaise raat ki poori tafri worth ho gayi. Coding ka tension aur allnighter dono hi Banaras ki student life ka permanent bhaukaal hai."
"Kal mock interview ka scene full drama tha. Pehle toh confident feel ho rahi thi, neatly dressed, resume ready, aur practice mode on. Jaise hi interview start hua, ekdum real mode mein shift ho gayaquestions ekdum chauchak type, aur dimag thoda blank. Ek question pe atki, doosra poochha, toh galti se answer gadbad kar diya. Hr ka expression dekha, lag raha tha poora kantaap mode on. Ek point pe toh boltebolte awkward silence aa gaya, aur andar se full matargasti chal rahi thiYaar, yeh kya bol diya? Friends ke suggestions yaad aaye, par tab toh bas panic hi panic. Behaviour aur body language pe dhyaan dene ki koshish ki, par voice thodi shaky ho gayi, smile bhi natural nahi lag rahi thi. Poora session ke end tak, kabhi lagta fail ho gayi, kabhi lagta thoda recover kar liya. Interview ke baad feedback milagaltiyan clearly highlight ki, aur improvement points bhi diye. Thoda embarrassment tha, par andar se samajh aaya ki mock hi toh hai, asli interview pe confidence milega. Raat ko laptop pe notes revise kiya, aur decide kiya next time poora ready rahungiquestions, answers aur poora attitude set. Banaras ki student life ka ye hi bhaukaalgaltiyan hoti hain, thoda bhasad hota hai, par seekh bhi full lallantop level ka milta hai."
