"Aaj finally thoda time nikal ke main Ganga kinare aa hi gayi. Room pe jo bhasad machi thi na exams ko leke, dimaag phat raha tha mera. Socha sab chhodchaad ke thoda sukoon dhoondhne aa jaun. Aur sach bataun? Yahan Assi ke kone wali seedhi pe baith ke jo feeling aa rahi hai, wo kisi 5star cafe mein nahi milti. Saamne paani ekdum shant hai, suraj dhal raha hai aur hawa ekdum lallantop chal rahi hai. Pata hai Diary, roz college mein hum log kitni bakaiti karte hain, futurefuture chillate hain, par yahan aake lagta hai ki yeh sab bas faltu ki magajmari hai. Leheron ko dekh ke lagta hai life bhi aise hi flow karni chahiye, hum bekar mein siyappa paal ke rakhte hain dimaag mein. Abhi ek naav nikli saamne se, usmein kuch tourists baithe the, bada bhaukaal tha unka camerawamera leke, par main apni is 50 rupaye wali diary aur pen ke saath hi zyada khush hun. Yahan baith ke likhna ek therapy jaisa hai. Saari tension, sara stress Ganga ji ne apne andar le liya jaise. Ab andhera ho raha hai, thodi der mein aarti ki taiyari ka taandav shuru hone wala hai aur bheed badhne wali hai. Chalo, ab uthti hun, Pappu ki dukan se ek kantaap chai piyungi aur phir wahi daily routine mein wapas. Par abhi ke liye, dil ekdum gardengarden ho gaya hai. Aaj ki shaam chauchak rahi!"
