"Arre sunn! Aaj shaam ko Godowlia taraf gayi thi, aur wahan pahunch ke Baba ki Thandai na piyein, aisa ho sakta hai kya? Humne full kulhad bharke MalaiKesar Thandai li. Bhai sahab, woh taste ekdum kantaap tha! Itni gaadhi aur dryfruits se bhari hui thi ki aadha pet toh wahin bhar gaya. Thandai peene ke baad jo sharir mein susti aayi, bas pucho mat. Main seedha Dashashwamedh Ghat ki taraf nikal gayi aur ek kone mein seedhiyon pe jaake baith gayi. Pata nahi uss Thandai ka asar tha ya Banaras ki hawa ka, par dimaag ekdum shant ho gaya. Main wahan ghanto baithi rahi bas Ganga ji ko dekhte hue. Aaspaas kitni bhagdad machi thiyatris ki bheed, panditon ke mantra, ghanti ki awaazeinpar mujhe sab kuch slow motion mein lag raha tha. Aisa lag raha tha main kisi aur hi zone mein hoon. Duniya bhar ki bakaiti aur college ki tension sab kalti maar gaye the dimaag se. Beechbeech mein thandi hawa chal rahi thi jo ekdum lallantop lag rahi thi face pe. Saamne se naav ja rahi thi, lights paani mein chamak rahi thi... pura nazara chauchak tha. Mann hi nahi kar raha tha uthne ka. Aisa lag raha tha bas yahin baithi rahun puri raat. Sach mein yaar, kabhi kabhi bas chupchap ghat pe baithna bhi best therapy hai!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj hum log Ghat kinare wale mele mein gaye the, aur wahan ka scene dekhne layak tha. Matlab pair rakhne ki jagah nahi thi, itni bhagdad machi hui thi. Hum log dhakke khate hue andar ghuse, par andar ka mahaul ekdum rangeela tha. Har taraf lights lagi thi, aur loud speaker pe jo purane gaane baj rahe the, uska alag hi bhaukaal tha. Sabse pehle toh humne wahan Break Dance wale jhule pe baithne ki galti kar di. Bhai, jab usne speed badhayi na, meri toh saans hi atak gayi! Riya mere bagal mein baith ke jo cheekh rahi thi, uski awaaz sunke neeche khade log bhi humari tafri lene lage. Par sach bataun, darr ke saath maza bhi chauchak aaya. Uske baad humne food stall pe dhava bola. Wahan ki chaat aur cholebhature ekdum kantaap the yaar! Garamgaram jalebi dekh ke toh raha hi nahi gaya, diet gayi bhaad mein. Humne wahan khade hoke full matargasti ki aur 23 plate uda diye. Wapsi mein patri (street) market se humne 5050 rupaye wale jhumke aur rings kharide. Bheed mein bhasad toh bahut thi, par saste mein shopping karke dil gardengarden ho gaya. Ab pair dukh rahe hain chalchal ke, par mela ghumne ka apna hi sukoon hai, pura mood fresh ho gaya!"
"Yaar, aaj shaam ko maine jo Assi pe time bitaya hai, bas pucho mat. Main seedha neeche wali seedhi pe jaake baith gayi aur apne pair Ganga ji ke paani mein latka diye. Paani itna thanda aur saaf tha ki jaise hi touch hua, puri din ki thakan gayab ho gayi. Wahan ka nazara ekdum lallantop tha. Ek taraf naav wale apni bakaiti kar rahe the, aur dusri taraf leheron ki halki awaaz. College mein din bhar jo coding aur assignments ki magajmari chalti hai na, yahan aake sab dimaag se nikal gaya. Aisa laga jaise main duniya ki saari bhasad se door aa gayi hoon, bas main aur Ganga ji. Mere bagal mein kuch bache paani uda rahe the, full matargasti mood mein. Unko dekh ke mera dil bhi gardengarden ho gaya. Sach bataun, pair paani mein daal ke ghanto baithna koi mamuli baat nahi hai, iska alag hi sukoon hai, ekdum kantaap therapy hai yeh. Mann toh kar raha tha ki hostel wapas hi na jaun, bas yahin shanti mein baithi rahun. Par phir warden ka darr yaad aaya toh majboori mein kalti maarni padi. Par kasam se, wo thande paani ka feel abhi tak yaad hai, aaj ki shaam ekdum chauchak thi!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj jo maine Sankat Mochan se Assi Ghat tak paidal march kiya hai na, kasam se pairon ki band baj gayi par dil khush ho gaya. Darshan karke nikle toh socha auto le lu, par phir socha chalo aaj thodi matargasti karte hue paidal hi chalte hain, mausam bhi lallantop tha. Lanka road pe jo bhasad mili hai bhai sahab! Rickshaw wale, auto wale, aur unke beech mein hum log raasta banate hue nikal rahe the. Bichbich mein dukano se garamagaram kachori ki khushbu aa rahi thi jo bada distract kar rahi thi, par hum date rahe. Raste bhar humne jo doston ke saath bakaiti ki hai traffic aur logo ko leke, time ka pata hi nahi chala. Assi pahunchne mein kareeb 20 minute lage honge, par jab wo bheedbhad se nikal ke ghat ki khuli hawa lagi chehre pe, toh saari thakan kalti maar gayi. Aisa laga jaise kisi dusri duniya mein aa gaye hon. Wahan pahunch ke seedha lemon tea li aur seedhiyon pe  gaye. Paid chalne ka apna hi maza hai Banaras mein, chahe bhagdad kitni bhi ho, galiyon aur sadkon ka feel ekdum chauchak rehta hai. Agli baar tu bhi chalna, pakka auto ke paise bachenge aur tafri bhi full hogi!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj humne jo doston ke saath milke Street Food Tour kiya hai na, pet toh bhar gaya par niyat nahi bhari. Plan ekdum chauchak banaya tha humne. Sabse pehle hum log Godowlia pahunche. Wahan hamesha ki tarah full bhasad machi thi, par humne dhakkamukki karke Kashi Chat Bhandar pe kabza jama hi liya. Bhai, wahan ki Tamatar Chat kha ke toh aatma tript ho gayi! Ekdum kantaap taste tha, masale aise ki dimaag khul jaye. Riya toh aur teekha, aur teekha kar rahi thi, baad mein pani ke liye bhagdad macha di usne. Uske baad humne socha thoda meetha ho jaye, toh humne auto kiya aur seedha Lanka pahunche Pahalwan Lassi pe. Wahan ki Malai Lassi... uff! Kulhad mein upar tak malai bhari thi, dekh ke hi dil gardengarden ho gaya. Peene ke baad jo neend aa rahi thi na, bas pucho mat, par humari matargasti abhi khatam nahi hui thi. Last mein hum ludhaktepudhakte Assi Ghat pahunche. Wahan Pizzeria Vaatika mein baith ke Apple Pie khayi. Ganga kinare thandi hawa, garam pie, aur doston ki bakaitipoora scene lallantop tha yaar. Pet itna tight ho gaya hai ki ab hostel tak paidal chalna padega digestion ke liye. Agli baar tu bhi chalna, bada bhaukaal maza aata hai in galiyon mein khane ka!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj mausam ne jo karvat li hai na, dil ekdum gardengarden ho gaya. Hum log Assi pe baithe the, socha tha thodi der sukoon se baithenge, par Indra Dev alag hi mood mein the. Achanak se jo kaale baadal aaye aur tez baarish shuru hui, bhai sahab, humein kalti maarne ka time hi nahi mila! Pure ghat pe achanak bhagdad mach gayi, sab idharudhar bhaagne lage chupne ke liye, par hum dheet wahin khade rahe. Pehle toh laga kapde kharab ho jayenge, par phir socha ab bheeg hi gaye hain toh full matargasti kar lete hain. Wo baarish mein ghat ka nazara ekdum lallantop tha. Ganga ji ke upar baarish ki boondein pad rahi thin aur hawa itni thandi thi ki maza aa gaya. Humne wahan bheegte hue jo bakaiti ki hai, aaspaas ke log humein pagal samajh rahe the, par hum apni hi dhun mein the. Mere naye shoes pure gile ho gaye, mummy ko pata chala toh ghar pe siyappa pakka hai, par us waqt scene ekdum chauchak tha. Wapas aate time sadak pe jo bhasad mili, auto milne mein badi magajmari hui. Rickshaw wale bhi double paise maang rahe the, bada bhaukaal dikha rahe the baarish ka. Par kasam se, hostel aake garam chai aur pakode khane ka jo sukoon mila, wo kantaap tha. Aaj ki shaam yaadgar ban gayi!"
"Yaar, aaj himmat karke main finally Manikarnika Ghat gayi. Sach bataun, pehle toh wahan ki bhasad aur wo aag dekh ke pair kaanp rahe the. Itni bodies, wo dhuwan, aur logon ka shor... starting mein laga galti kar di yahan aake. Par phir main ek kone mein chupchap khadi ho gayi. Wahan ka bhaukaal hi alag hai yaar. Ek pal mein laga ki hum log roz kitni faltu bakaiti karte hainassignments, placements, breakup... sab yahan aake zero lagta hai. Jab wo chita jalti hui dekhi, toh dimaag mein ekdum sannata cha gaya. Laga ki end mein sab yahi hai, toh itna ego aur ghamand kyun? Log kehte hain wahan negative vibes hain, par mujhe ek ajeeb sa sukoon mila. Jaise life ka sabse kantaap sach saamne aa gaya ho. Wapas aate time main aur Riya pure raste chup the, koi tafri nahi, koi matargasti nahi. Bas wo visual dimaag se nahi nikal raha. Life bahut choti hai yaar, faltu ki magajmari chhod ke khul ke jeena chahiye. Aaj ka experience heavy tha par zaroori tha."
"Arre sunn! Aaj subah jo himmat karke 4 baje uthi hoon na, uska fal mil gaya mujhe. Hum log Ravidas Ghat gaye the sunrise dekhne. Assi pe toh hamesha bhasad machi rehti hai, par Ravidas Ghat subahsubah ekdum shant tha, koi magajmari nahi. Jaise hi suraj nikalna shuru hua, bhai sahab, Ganga ji ka paani sona jaisa chamakne laga. Woh nazara itna lallantop tha ki neend ki saari thakan kalti maar gayi. Thandi hawa chal rahi thi jo chehre pe lag ke dil gardengarden kar rahi thi. Humne wahan baith ke jo sukoon mehsoos kiya, wo hostel ki daily life mein kahan milta hai. Mere saath Waleed aur Priya the, shuru mein toh woh neend mein bakaiti kar rahe the ki kyun uthaya itni jaldi, par nazara dekh ke unka bhi mood chauchak ho gaya. Humne wahan baith ke kulhad wali chai pi, jo ekdum kantaap lagi uss mausam mein. Wahan kuch log yoga kar rahe the, unka alag hi bhaukaal tha. Humne bhi socha try karein, par humse toh stretching mein hi matargasti shuru ho gayi. Photos li, thodi der shanti se baithe, aur phir wapas college ki taraf nikal liye. Din ki shuruat aaj ekdum perfect hui hai!"
"Oye sunn! Aaj humne jo Godowlia ki patli galiyon mein bhulbhulaiya khela hai na, mazaa aa gaya par pairon ki band baj gayi. Hum log Kachori Gali se andar ghuse the, socha tha shortcut marenge, par wahan itni bhasad machi thi ki aadha time toh dhakkamukki mein nikal gaya. Upar se wo scooter wale bhaiya log itni patli gali mein bhi full speed mein horn bajate hue nikalte hain, alag hi bhaukaal hai unka. Ghumteghumte jab thak gaye toh humne socha, Bhai Banaras mein hain aur Paan nahi khaya toh kya kiya? Hum ek purani si dukan pe ruke aur bhaiya ko bola, Ekdum chauchak meetha paan lagaiye. Bhaiya ne jo bade pyaar se gulukand aur chatni daal ke gilouri banayi na... uff! Jaise hi muh mein paan dala, kasam se dimaag ke saare fuse jud gaye. Swad ekdum kantaap tha! Muh itna bhar gaya tha ki bolna mushkil tha, hum bas ek dusre ko dekh ke matargasti wali hasi has rahe the. Woh thandithandi feeling aur wo mithas... saari thakan minute mein kalti maar gayi. Uske baad humne muh laal karke jo tashan mein wapsi ki hai, feel aa rahi thi ki hum hi is sheher ke nawab hain. Sach mein yaar, galiyon mein dhakke khane ke baad wo paan khana, feeling ekdum lallantop thi!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj subah humne neend ki qurbani di aur seedha Godowlia pahunch gaye, kyunki sardiyan aa gayi hain aur Malaiyyo nahi khaya toh kya khaaya! Bhai, Thatheri Bazar wali gali mein ghuste hi jo kesar ki khushbu aayi, dimaag wahi set ho gaya tha. Galiyon mein subahsubah bhi itni bhasad machi thi, sabko Malaiyyo hi chahiye tha. Humne badi mushkil se jagah banayi aur bhaiya ko bola, Ek bada kulhad lagaiye, dry fruits daba ke. Jaise hi woh peelipeeli jhaag (foam) wala kulhad haath mein aaya, dil gardengarden ho gaya. Chamach muh mein daalte hi woh gayab! Matlab, kya chauchak cheez hai yaar, hawa kha rahe ho jaise, par taste ekdum lallantop. Mithaas bhi ekdum balanced, aur upar se wo pistebadam ka bhaukaal. Humne wahan khade hoke pehle ek khaya, phir raha nahi gaya toh dusra bhi order kar diya. Meri friend Riya toh bol rahi thi pack kara ke hostel le chalte hain, par maine bola, Pagal hai kya? Yeh Malaiyyo hai, hostel pahunchte tak hawa ho jayega. Humne wahin full matargasti ki, photos click ki, aur pet bhar ke kantaap swad liya. Subah ki thand mein Malaiyyo khane ka sukoon hi alag hai, neend kharab karna safal ho gaya aaj!"
"Arre sunn! Aaj shaam ko humne finally wo boat ride wala plan execute kar hi diya. Hum sab Assi Ghat pahunche aur ek badi waali naav pakdi. Manjhi kaka se rate ko leke thodi magajmari hui pehle, wo bada bhaukaal dikha rahe the, par humne bhi bargaining karke set kar liya. Jaise hi boat beech Ganga mein pahunchi... bhai sahab, wo nazara! Suraj dhal raha tha aur pura aasmaan orange aur pink ho gaya tha. Paani mein jo reflection aa raha tha na, ekdum lallantop lag raha tha. Ghat pe door se lights aur aarti ki bhasad dikh rahi thi, par hum paani ke beech ekdum shanti mein the. Thandi hawa chal rahi thi, dil gardengarden ho gaya. Humne wahan jam ke bakaiti ki, Riya ne toh Titanic pose maarne ki koshish ki, humne uski itni tafri li ki wo sharam ke maare baith gayi. Birds bhi ud rahe the saathsaath, scene ekdum filmi tha. Maine itni photos li hain ki phone ki storage full ho gayi hai. Sach mein, wo sunset aur wo sukoon... mood ekdum chauchak ho gaya. Aisa lag raha tha time wahin ruk jaye aur hum wapas us siyappa bhari duniya mein na jayein. Best shaam thi yaar ye!"
"Assi ki shaam ka toh alag hi bhaukaal hai. Bheed hoti hai, shor hota hai, par phir bhi insaan wahan akele sukoon se reh sakta hai. Maine bhi kayi baar yeh kiya hai. Jab hostel mein roommates ki bakaiti aur padhai ka tension sar pe chadhta hai, toh main bhi chupchap nikal leti hoon. Wahan seedhiyon pe baith ke bas logon ko aatejaate dekhna bhi ek timepass hai. Koi guitar baja raha hota hai, koi deep discussion mein magajmari kar raha hota hai, aur foreign tourists ka apna alag hi scene chalta hai. Hawa thandi lagti hai toh mann ekdum gardengarden ho jata hai. Maine toh wahan ki Lemon Tea piye bina wapas nahi aati. Hath mein garam chai ka kulhad ho, saamne Ganga ji hon, aur kaan mein halka sa aarti ka shor... bhai sahab, feeling ekdum lallantop hoti hai. Aisa lagta hai saare siyappe wahi paani mein beh gaye. Akela feel hua ya maza aaya khud ki company mein? Kyunki sach bataun, Assi pe banda kabhi akela nahi hota, poora sheher saath hota hai. Mood fresh karke wapas hostel aane ka tashan hi alag hota hai phir!"
"Sahi kaha yaar! Dashashwamedh ki Aarti dekh ke toh patthar dil bhi pighal jaye. Wo experience hi aisa hai ki romrom khada ho jata hai. Maine bhi jab pehli baar dekhi thi, toh main bas dekhti hi reh gayi thi. Wo 7 pandit jab ek saath badebade deepak uthate hain, aur peeche se wo ghanti aur damru ki awaaz aati hai... bhai sahab, wo bhaukaal hi alag hota hai. Aisa lagta hai saari duniya ka focus bas wahi ek jagah pe hai. Aur sabse best part pata hai kya lagta hai? Jab wo Shankh Naad (conch shell blowing) hota hai. Us time pure ghat pe jo sannata chaata hai aur bas shankh ki awaaz gunjti hai, kasam se, dimaag sunn ho jata hai. Dil ekdum gardengarden ho jata hai wo divine energy feel karke. Wahan ki bheed aur bhasad bhi us time feel nahi hoti. Sab log bas haath jode khade hote hain, chahe boat pe hon ya seedhiyon pe. Wo mahaul itna chauchak hota hai ki insaan apni saari tension, saare siyappe bhool jata hai. Aisa lagta hai bas yahi sach hai, baaki sab mohmaya hai. Aarti khatam hone ke baad jo shanti milti hai na, wo kisi aur jagah nahi mil sakti. Ekdum lallantop feeling hoti hai, hai na?"
"Yaar, aaj dil ka pura satyanaash ho gaya. Tujhe pata hai na wo Rohan? Civil department wala, jiska pura college mein alag hi bhaukaal hai? Aaj subah se main uske liye full ready hoke, wo nayi jhumki pehen ke gayi thi. Socha tha VT (Vishwanath Temple) pe milenge toh thodi matargasti hogi, shayad cold coffee peene chalenge. Wahan pahunchi toh pehle toh itni bhagdad machi thi, par jaise hi usne mujhe dekha, meri heartbeat fast ho gayi. Laga aaj toh scene chauchak hone wala hai. Wo paas aaya, smile kiya... aur bola, Aur bhai, kya haal hai? Notes milenge kya DSA ke? Matlab... seriously? Main yahan lallantop ban ke khadi hun aur isko notes ki padi hai? Chalo, wahan tak bhi theek tha. Par phir usne jo bakaiti shuru ki na, dimaag kharab ho gaya. 15 minute tak bas cricket aur politics jhaadta raha. Main soch rahi thi koi compliment dega, par banda alag hi zone mein tha. Aur sunn, hadd toh tab ho gayi jab jaatejaate bola, Yaar wo teri friend Riya single hai kya? Kasam se, mann kiya wahin ek kheech ke kantaap lagaun! Dil ke tukde karke banda kalti maar liya. Ab main yahan Assi pe baith ke chai pi rahi hun aur soch rahi hun ki ladke itne buddhu kyun hote hain. Pura mood off hai, ab tu aaja jaldi, thodi tafri maarenge tabhi theek hungi main."
"Yaar, dimaag ka dahi hua pada hai aaj. Dil mein ek ajeeb sa siyappa chal raha hai. Socha tha kalti maar dungi uski yaadon se, move on kar lungi, par kambakht dimaag se nikal hi nahi raha. Kal tak jiske saath hum Lanka pe Lassi peete hue duniya bhar ki bakaiti karte the, aaj uska Last Seen check karke hi kaam chalana pad raha hai. Maine aaj janbujh ke doston ke saath matargasti karne ka plan banaya, socha thoda mood chauchak ho jayega. Par wahan har dusra ladka uski tarah dikh raha tha. Koi bike pe bhaukaal maar ke nikla toh ek second ke liye dhadkan ruk gayi, laga wahi hai. Khud pe itna gussa aa raha hai na, mann kar raha hai sheeshe mein dekh ke khud ko hi ek kantaap laga loon. Wo shayad wahan apni life mein mast hoga, kisi aur ke saath tafri maar raha hoga, aur main yahan Devdas bani ghum rahi hoon. Logic kehta hai Bhaad mein jaaye woh, par dil hai ki manta hi nahi. Uski wo faltu jokes, wo bina baat ki hassi, aur wo saath mein ghat pe bitaye hue sham... sab flashback ki tarah chal raha hai aankhon ke saamne. Pata hai main stupid sound kar rahi hoon, par kya karun? Miss toh kar rahi hoon yaar. Ab tu jaldi aa ja, Assi chalte hain. Ganga kinare shanti se baith ke hi shayad ye dil ke andar ki bhasad shant hogi."
