"Oye, mat puch kal raat ka haal. Neend ne toh jaise mere room se kalti hi maar li thi. Puri raat main bas bistar pe karwatein badalti rahi aur chhat (ceiling) ko ghoorti rahi. Dimaag mein bas wahi ek insan ghum raha tha, jaise koi 24hour movie chal rahi ho. Kabhi main soch rahi thi ki hamari agli mulaqat kaisi hogi, kabhi main khud hi mann mein future ki bakaiti kar rahi thiki hum saath mein Assi pe ghumenge, wo mujhe bike pe bithake bhaukaal maarega. Matlab, maine puri script likh dali dimaag mein! Ek point pe laga ki so jaati hun varna subah class mein satyanaash ho jayega. Par jaise hi aankh band karu, uski smile saamne aa jaye aur dil zorzor se matargasti karne lage. Pet mein wo ajeeb si gudgudi ho rahi thi jo sone hi nahi de rahi thi. Subah jab mummy ne uthaya, toh meri aankhein aisi sooji hui thi jaise main kisi jung se aayi hun. Mummy ne pucha, Raat bhar kya kar rahi thi?, maine jhooth bol diya Assignment ki magajmari kar rahi thi. Ab darr lag raha hai ki kahin class mein neend aa gayi aur sir ne pakad liya toh tafri ban jayegi. Par sach bataun? Ye thakan bhi lallantop lag rahi hai kyunki wajah wo hai. Ye ek tarfa pyaar ka siyappa insaan ko ullu bana deta hai yaar, par feeling badi kantaap hoti hai!"
