"Arre sunn! Aaj toh life set ho gayi hai meri. Subah se jo practical ka siyappa chal raha tha dimaag mein, wo ek second mein hawa ho gaya. Main corridor se bhagebhage ja rahi thi, lab file submit karne ki bhagdad machi thi. Aur tabhi... samne se wo aa raha tha. Yaar, uska wo simple shirt mein aana hi apne aap mein bhaukaal hai. Par aaj toh hadd hi ho gayi. Jaise hi hum cross hue, usne meri taraf dekha, eye contact hua... aur usne smile kiya! Kasam se, main toh wahin pighal ke paani ho gayi. Aisa laga background mein violin bajne lage hain. Wo smile itni chauchak thi ki main agle 10 minute tak bina wajah hehe kar rahi thi. Jo pairon mein thakan thi, wo turant kalti maar gayi. Abhi library mein baithi hun, kitab khuli hai par akshar naach rahe hain. Pura din bas gardengarden feeling aa rahi hai. Riya puch rahi hai Tu pagal ho gayi hai kya jo akele muskura rahi hai?, par usko kya pata ki dil ka mausam kitna lallantop ho gaya hai aaj. Lagta hai aaj raat neend nahi aayegi, bas wahi 2 second ka scene yaad karke dimaag mein matargasti chalti rahegi. Aaj ka din toh official wala Happy Day declare kar diya maine!"
"Arre yaar, mat puch aaj ka scene! Aaj canteen ka dosa bhale hi thanda tha, par nazara ekdum lallantop tha. Main wahan lecture ke baad full bore hoke sannata kaat rahi thi, ki achanak se canteen ke darwaze pe bhaukaal entry hui uski. Bhai, wo bas doston ke saath chai peene aaya tha, par jis style se banda khada tha na, kasam se, mera dil wahin gardengarden ho gaya. Canteen mein itni bhasad machi thi, log chilla rahe the, par mujhe bas wahi dikh raha tha. Aisa lag raha tha baaki sab log blur ho gaye hain, bas spotlight uspe hai. Usne jab hass ke apne dost ko thappad mara na, toh yahan mere chehre pe apne aap wo stupid wali smile aa gayi. Riya ne mujhe notice kar liya aur wahi shuru ho gayi uski bakaitiOye, sambhal ja, aankhein bahar aa jayengi. Maine usko table ke neeche se laat maari ki chup reh, warna tafri ban jayegi meri. Par sach bataun? Wo 10 minute jo wo wahan tha, mera mood ekdum chauchak ho gaya. Subah se jo assignments ka siyappa sar pe chadha tha, wo sab gayab. Ab toh bas wahi chai peeta hua uska chehra dimaag mein ghum raha hai. Lagta hai aaj bhookhpyaas sab kalti maar gayi hai, pet bas khushi se bhar gaya hai!"
"Assi Ghat ki seedhiyon pe baithi hun, aur mere aaspaas duniya bhar ki bhasad machi hai. Log hans rahe hain, groups mein matargasti kar rahe hain, guitar baj raha hai... sabka mood ekdum chauchak hai. Par sach bataun? Mujhe ye sab dekh ke aur zyada ghutan ho rahi hai. Aisa lag raha hai ki main kisi invisible kaanch ke dabbe mein band hun. Bahar sab rangbiranga hai, sab lallantop hai, par mere andar ek ajeeb sa sannata phaila hua hai. Jiske chehre pe dekho, wo khush dikh raha hai, apni life mein set lag raha hai. Aur ek main hun, jo yahan bheed mein baith ke bhi akela feel kar rahi hun. Dimaag mein itne siyappe chal rahe hain ki chai ka swaad bhi feeka lag raha hai. Riya aur baaki sab Selfie! Selfie! chillake bakaiti kar rahe hain, aur main bas zabardasti ke daant dikha rahi hun taaki koi puche na ki Kya hua? Kyunki agar kisi ne puch liya, toh shayad main yahin ro dungi. Bura lagta hai yaar jab aapke andar toofan ho aur bahar sab shant dikhana pade. Aisa lagta hai sab aage nikal gaye, apni life mein bhaukaal macha rahe hain, aur main wahin purani baaton aur purane dard mein atki hui hun. Mann kar raha hai yahan se kalti maar lun aur kambal odh ke so jaun, kyunki ye duniya ki khushi aaj mujhe chub rahi hai. Dil ka haal ekdum falooda ban chuka hai, aur kisi ko khabar tak nahi hai."
"Yaar, aaj mood ka pura satyanaash ho gaya hai. Socha tha Chacha ke ghar dinner pe jaungi toh thoda mind fresh hoga, par wahan toh alag hi siyappa khada ho gaya. Baat shuru hui normal padhai se, aur phir Bua ji ne wahi purana raag chhed diyacomparison ka. Unhone bhari mehfil mein meri cousin, Ananya, ki taareefon ke pul baandhne shuru kar diye. Dekho Ananya ko, Bangalore mein job lag gayi, package dekho uska, kya bhaukaal life hai uski. Aur tum? Abhi tak bas college ke chakkar kaat rahi ho? Kasam se, us waqt aisa laga jaise kisi ne dil pe zor se kantaap mara ho. Main yahan roz coding ki magajmari kar rahi hun, projects mein dimaag khapa rahi hun, par unko wo mehnat dikhti hi nahi. Unki wo 5 minute ki bakaiti ne mere pure confidence ka falooda bana diya. Sabke saamne toh maine jabardasti ki smile chipka li, par andar se jo ghutan ho rahi thi na, bata nahi sakti. Aisa lag raha tha ki main enough nahi hun. Chahe main kitna bhi chauchak perform kar lun, inke liye main hamesha Ananya se neeche hi rahungi. Wahan se toh jaldi kalti maar li maine sar dard ka bahana banake, par ab hostel room ke sannate mein wo saari baatein kaan mein gunj rahi hain. Ankhon se aansu ruk nahi rahe hain yaar. Bura tab nahi lagta jab duniya ungli uthati hai, bura tab lagta hai jab apne hi log aapko ehsaas dilate hain ki aap kisi race mein piche reh gaye ho. Aaj andar se pura khali feel ho raha hai. Would you like me to write a scene where she looks at her coding project on the laptop and feels like deleting it all in frustration, or a scene where she calls her mom to cry but ends up pretending everything is fine to not worry her?"
"Raat ke 2 baj rahe hain, pura hostel gehri neend mein hai, aur bas ek main hun jo yahan chhat ki paani wali tanki ke peeche chupke apne aansuon se lad rahi hun. Sheher mein sannata phaila hua hai, par mere dimaag mein jo shor hai, wo shant hi nahi ho raha. Din bhar toh doston ke beech bada cool aur strong rehne ka bhaukaal maintain karti hun. Sabko lagta hai meri life ekdum lallantop chal rahi hai, par andar hi andar jo ghutan ho rahi hai, wo kisko dikhaun? Jab tak light on rehti hai, tab tak jabardasti ki hassi chipkani padti hai, par ab andhere mein wo mask utaar ke asliyat saamne aa gayi hai. Aaj achanak se sab kuch bahut bhari lagne laga. Career ka tension, ghar walon ki umeed, aur wo purane rishton ka dard jo kabhi kalti nahi maarta... sab ek saath hit kiya. Aisa lag raha hai life ka pura falooda ban chuka hai aur main bas sametne ki koshish kar rahi hun. Muh pe haath rakh ke ro rahi hun taaki sisakne ki awaaz se koi jag na jaye. Agar kisi ne dekh liya toh kal phir wahi Kya hua? wale sawalon ka siyappa shuru ho jayega, aur mujhe abhi kisi ko explanation nahi dena. Ganga ji ki taraf se thandi hawa aa rahi hai, par wo bhi aaj sukoon nahi de rahi. Bas aisa lag raha hai ki main is bheed bhare sheher mein bilkul akeli reh gayi hun. Rona aa raha hai apni hi haalat pe, ki kaise main apni feelings ke saath bakaiti kar rahi hunduniya ke liye khush, aur khud ke liye itni hollow. Bas dil halka karne ki koshish hai, taaki kal subah phir se nakli muskurahat pehen sakun."
"Yaar, aaj aisa lag raha hai jaise main apne hi group mein Guest Appearance dene aayi hun. Hum log Lanka pe VT mein baithe the, socha tha purani tarah bakaiti hogi, par yahan toh scene hi badal gaya hai. Riya aur Sneha aapas mein hi khusurpusur kar rahi hain, apne inside jokes pe has rahi hain, aur main bas wahan baith ke zabardasti smile kar rahi hun taaki out of place feel na karun. Beech mein maine ek baar topic change karne ki koshish ki, thoda bhaukaal jamane ka try kiya, par unhone meri baat aise ignore ki jaise main invisible hun. Sabse zyada bura tab laga jab wo log weekend ka plan bana rahe theArre wahan chalenge, bahut lallantop jagah haiaur mujhe pucha tak nahi. Aisa laga jaise main unke future plans ka hissa hi nahi hun ab. Ye wahi log hain jinke saath kabhi ek minute ka sannata nahi hota tha, aur aaj humare beech itni diwaarein aa gayi hain. Main wahan baith ke bas straw chaba rahi thi aur phone mein scroll karne ki acting kar rahi thi taaki unhe ye na lage ki main akela feel kar rahi hun. Aisa lag raha hai ki dheeredheere main side hoti ja rahi hun aur inka group mere bina bhi pura hai. Ye realization ki ab aap apne best friends ki priority nahi rahe... dil ka pura falooda bana deta hai yaar. Mann kar raha hai ab chupchap yahan se kalti maar lun, kyunki ye begaani bheed ab bardasht nahi ho rahi."
"Yaar, aaj gali mein ek stray puppy ko apni poonch ke peeche golgol ghumte dekha, aur dil ka pura satyanaash ho gaya. Mujhe turant Bruno ki yaad aa gayi. Ab wo hamare beech nahi hai, ye baat dimaag maan leta hai, par dil aaj bhi darwaze pe uski aahat dhoondta hai. Pehle jab main college se thakihaari, duniya bhar ki magajmari jhel ke wapas aati thi, toh wo gate pe hi milta tha. Chahe mera mood kitna bhi kharab ho, uska wo poonch hilana aur mujhpe koodna... saara stress minute mein kalti maar jata tha. Uski bakaiti pure ghar mein raunak rakhti thikabhi mummy ki chappal chura ke bhaagna, kabhi doodh ke liye kitchen mein bhaukaal machana. Ab ghar ghusti hun toh bas ek ajeeb sa sannata kaatne ko daudta hai. Wo corner jahan wo sota tha, ab khali pada hai. Kabhikabhi aadat se wahan nazar jaati hai, lagta hai abhi uth ke aayega aur mere haath chatne lagega, par phir reality hit karti hai aur dil ka falooda ban jata hai. Log kehte hain jaanwar hi toh tha, par wo sirf jaanwar nahi tha yaar, mera sabse loyal dost tha. Jab main roti thi, toh bina kuch bole wo apna sar meri god mein rakh deta tha. Aaj aankhein bhari hui hain, par aansu pochne ke liye wo gila naak wala chehra paas nahi hai. Zindagi ki iss bhasad mein wo ek sukoon tha jo chala gaya. Aisa lagta hai ghar ka ek hissa toot gaya hai jo ab kabhi judega nahi. Bahut khalikhali lag raha hai aaj."
"Aaj Assi ki unhi seedhiyon pe, jahan humesha sukoon milta tha, aaj wahan baith ke dam ghut raha tha. Main pichle do ghante se wahan akeli baithi thi, haath mein thandi ho chuki chai ka kulhad liye, bas Ganga ji ke paani ko ghoor rahi thi. Aaspaas duniya bhar ki bhasad machi thi. Log aarti ke liye ikkattha ho rahe the, guitar baj raha tha, doston ke groups full matargasti kar rahe the. Par un sabke shor ke beech, mere andar ek ajeeb sa sannata tha jo cheekh raha tha. Sabke chehre kitne lallantop lag rahe the, sab khush the, aur ek main thi jo bheed mein baith ke bhi akela feel kar rahi thi. Dimaag mein itne siyappe chal rahe hain ki samajh nahi aa raha life kis direction mein ja rahi hai. Kabhi future ka dar, kabhi purani yaadon ka kalesh. Aisa lag raha tha ki main bas act kar rahi hun normal hone ka. Agar koi galti se bhi puch leta Tu theek hai?, toh shayad wahin raita phail jata aur main ro deti. Log kehte hain Ganga kinare saare dukh beh jaate hain, par aaj mera dil itna bhari tha ki lehrein bhi use halka nahi kar payi. Mann kiya ki cheekh ke ro dun taaki ye andar ka guabar nikal jaye, par phir logon ki tafri banne ke darr se chup rahi. Aakhir mein jab bardasht nahi hua, toh chupchap uth ke wahan se kalti maar li. Wapas aate hue raste bhar aankhein dhundli thi, par kisi ko dikhaya nahi. Aaj Assi ne bhi mujhe khali haath lauta diya yaar."
"Yaar, aaj ghar ki diwaron se dum ghut raha hai. Abhi drawing room se MummyPapa ki aawazein aa rahi thin, aur topic wahi tha jiska mujhe sabse zyada darr thaMeri Shaadi. Mujhe laga tha abhi toh bas BCA khatam hone wala hai, thoda time milega MCA ya job ke liye. Maine socha tha abhi toh life ki asli matargasti shuru hui hai, apne dam pe kuch bhaukaal machana hai. Par yahan toh alag hi siyappa shuru ho gaya hai. Papa keh rahe the, Ladka wellsettled hai, sarkari naukri hai, haath se nikal gaya toh pachtayenge. Mera mann kiya ki cheekh ke bolun ki mujhe kisi aur ke settled hone se kya farak padta hai? Mujhe khud settle hona hai! Par himmat hi nahi hui. Unki nazron mein meri coding, mere projects, meri raatraat bhar ki magajmari... sab bekaar hai. Unke liye meri degree bas ek qualification hai jo shaadi ke card pe chauchak lagegi. Andar se itna khali feel ho raha hai na. Aisa lag raha hai jaise mere sapno ka falooda banaya ja raha hai aur main bas chupchap dekh rahi hun. Mere doston ke plans hainBangalore jaana hai, startup kholna hai. Aur yahan meri kismat ka faisla chaisamosa khate hue liya ja raha hai. Abhi laptop khol ke baithi hun, screen pe code hai par dimaag mein bas wahi Log kya kahenge aur Umar ho rahi hai wali bakaiti gunj rahi hai. Kamre mein AC chal raha hai par phir bhi paseene chhoot rahe hain. Aisa lag raha hai ki meri pehchan, meri identity, sab dheeredheere kalti maar rahi hai, aur main ek decorative piece ban ke reh jaungi. Aaj sach mein dil bahut bhari hai yaar."
"Yaar, aaj lag raha hai ki main kisi layak hi nahi hun. Itni mehnat ki thi, raaton ko jagjag ke DSA ki magajmari ki thi, socha tha aaj interview mein bhaukaal macha dungi. Par result ne meri aukaat dikha di. Jab HR ne wo tricky sawal pucha, toh main blank ho gayi. Aisa laga dimaag ka pura falooda ban gaya hai. Jo cheezein neend mein bhi bol sakti thi, wahan zubaan hi nahi khuli. Meri saari tayari, saara confidence wahin kalti maar gaya. Sabse zyada takleef tab hui jab bahar aake dekha ki Riya aur Amit select ho gaye. Wo log khushi se chillake matargasti kar rahe the, Party bhai party! kar rahe the. Aur main? Main bas zabardasti ki smile chipkake Congratulations bol rahi thi, jabki andar se dil cheekh ke rona chahta tha. Ghar pe mummy ne phone karke pucha, Beta kaisa hua?, toh main bol hi nahi paayi. Jhooth bol diya ki Abhi result nahi aaya aur phone kaat diya. Ab room ke sannate mein baith ke khud ko kos rahi hun. Lag raha hai main sabse peeche reh gayi hun. Kya faayda hua itni coding seekhne ka jab mauke pe siyappa hi hona tha? Aaj wo Failure wala tag bahut bhaari lag raha hai seene pe. Aisa lag raha hai sapne toot ke bikhar gaye hain aur main bas unke tukde utha rahi hun. Confidence ka pura satyanaash ho gaya hai yaar."
"Yaar, aaj dil ekdum baith gaya hai mera. Maine bade chaav se Mummy ko phone milaya tha, socha tha bataungi ki aaj mess mein khana kitna bakwaas tha aur thodi bakaiti karungi. Par phone uthate hi jo sunai diya, usne mere pairon tale zameen khiska di. Mummy shayaad phone utha ke side mein rakhna bhool gayi thi, aur wahan Papa ke saath unka kalesh chal raha tha. Awaazein itni tez thi ki phone speaker pe na hone ke bawajood sab saaf sunai de raha tha. Wahi purani baatein, wahi paison ki magajmari, aur ek dusre ko blame karne ka silsila. Main yahan hostel ke kamre mein sunn ho ke baithi thi, haath mein phone pakde, bas Hello? Hello? bolne ki koshish kar rahi thi, par meri awaaz un tak pahunch hi nahi rahi thi. Unki chikhpukar sunke aisa laga jaise koi mera kaleja nichod raha hai. Hamesha lagta tha ki main ghar se door hun toh shayaad wahan sab shant hoga, par aaj pata chala ki ye sannata bas meri taraf tha. Jab Papa ne gusse mein kuch bola aur Mummy rone lagi, toh mujhse bardasht nahi hua. Maine phone kaat diya. Par ab uss Call Ended screen ko ghoorte hue jo ghutan ho rahi hai na, bata nahi sakti."
"Yaar, aaj Godowlia mein achanak school wali Neha takra gayi. Socha tha gale lag ke wahi purani bakaiti karenge, school ke dino jaisa shor machayenge, par wahan toh scene hi badal chuka tha. Wo ab waisi nahi rahi. Mehange kapde, haath mein branded bags, aur baat karne ka tareeka... uff! Aisa lag raha tha main kisi stranger se mil rahi hun. Jab maine pucha, Aur bata, kaisi hai?, toh usne bas uparupar se jawab diya aur apni nayi highclass life ka bhaukaal dikhane lagi. Hum jo kabhi sadak kinare khade hoke 10 rupaye ke golgappe khate the aur matargasti karte the, aaj wo mujhe aise dekh rahi thi jaise main uske standard ki nahi hun. Usne meri simple kurti ko ek scanning nazar se dekha, aur kasam se, us ek nazar ne mujhe itna chhota feel karaya ki bata nahi sakti. Baatcheet mein wo sannata tha jo pehle kabhi nahi hota tha. 5 minute mein hi usne ghadi dekhi aur Getting late bolke kalti maar li. Main wahin khadi reh gayi, bheed ke beech akeli. Ghar aake purani photos dekh rahi hun aur rona aa raha hai. Hum wahi hain, sheher wahi hai, par dosti ka falooda ban gaya. Bura lagta hai jab koi apna itna aage nikal jaye ki aapko pehchanna hi bhool jaye. Aaj dosti haar gayi yaar."
"Yaar, aaj subah se phone haath mein leke baithi hun, par ring bajne se bhi darr lag raha hai. Jab se Mummy ka call aaya hai ki Dadi hospital mein hain, tab se mere andar ka sab kuch hil gaya hai. Yahan hostel mein sannata hai, par dimaag mein itna shor hai ki main paagal ho jaungi. Mujhe Dadi ki wo jhurriyon wali smile yaad aa rahi hai. Kaise jab Papa daantte the, toh wo dhaal banke saamne khadi ho jaati thi. Mere bachhe ko koi kuch nahi bolegaunki wo awaaz kaan mein gunj rahi hai. Aaj wahi Dadi ICU ke bed pe hain, aur main yahan door baithi coding aur assignments ki bekar si magajmari mein phasi hun. Aisa lag raha hai ki main kitni selfish hun, apni degree ke chakkar mein unke paas bhi nahi hun. Yaad hai jab main chhuttiyon mein ghar jaati thi? Wo chupke se mere haath mein 500 ka note thama deti thi aur kehti thi, Ja beta, apni pasand ka kuch kha lena. Aaj wo note mere wallet mein rakha hai, par use kharch karne ki himmat nahi ho rahi. Mann kar raha hai sab chhodchaad ke abhi ghar bhaag jaun, bas unke pair pakad ke baith jaun. Negative thoughts dimaag mein bhagdad macha rahe hainagar unhe kuch ho gaya toh? Ye khayal aate hi saans atak jaati hai. Life ka satyanaash lag raha hai bina unke. Bas bhagwan se prayer kar rahi hun ki ye bura waqt jaldi kalti maar le aur wo wapas ghar aa jayein. Aaj bohot akela lag raha hai yaar."
"Yaar, aaj life ne ek bahut bada reality check de diya. Raat ke 12 baje se main phone ko aise ghoor rahi thi jaise koi miracle hone wala hai. Socha tha notifications ki bhasad machegi, group mein video calls aayenge, status lagenge... par yahan toh maut ka sannata chhaya hua hai. Sirf Mummy ka call aaya subah. Unki awaaz sunke main ro padi, par control kar liya taaki unhe shak na ho. Unhone pucha Kya plan hai beta? Doston ke saath party karogi?, aur maine jhooth bol diya ki Haan Mummy, bahut bhaukaal plan hai. Asliyat ye hai ki main hostel room mein akeli baithi hun. Jin doston ke birthdays pe main raat bhar jag ke surprises plan karti thi, gift ki magajmari karti thi, aaj unhi doston ke Instagram stories pe full matargasti chal rahi haimemes share ho rahe hain, reels dali ja rahi hainpar kisi ko yaad tak nahi ki aaj mera birthday hai. Aisa lag raha hai jaise main invisible hun. Kya main itni unimportant hun ki ek Happy Birthday text bhi deserve nahi karti? Dil ka pura satyanaash ho gaya hai aaj. Mann kar raha hai apna phone switch off karke phenk dun. Log kehte hain dosti duniya ka sabse khoobsurat rishta hai, par aaj wahi rishta mere gale mein phande jaisa lag raha hai. Cake toh door ki baat, yahan izzat ka hi falooda ban gaya. Aaj ka din meri life ka sabse akela din hai yaar."
"Yaar, aaj toh aisa lag raha hai jaise kismat ne munh pe thappad maar diya ho. Scholarship ki list mein apna naam na dekh kar dimaag ekdum sunn ho gaya hai. Maine itni umeed lagayi thi ki ye mil jayegi toh ghar walon ka bojh thoda kam ho jayega, par yahan toh pura siyappa ho gaya. Hostel ke kamre mein baithi hun aur Papa ka chehra yaad aa raha hai. Kaise wo khet aur ghar ke kharchon mein katauti karke meri fees bharte hain. Maine socha tha iss baar unhe phone karke khushkhabri dungi ki Papa, ab aapko chinta karne ki zaroorat nahi, par ab toh unhe batane ki himmat bhi nahi ho rahi. Ghar pe pehle hi paison ki magajmari chalti rehti hai, aur ab ye fees ka naya pahaad. Aisa lag raha hai jaise main unke liye bas ek kharcha banke reh gayi hun. Mere doston ko farak nahi padta, wo toh apni matargasti mein lage hain, unke liye fees bas ek number hai. Par mere liye? Mere liye ye Papa ki dinraat ki mehnat hai jiska aaj maine satyanaash kar diya. Mann kar raha hai ki sab chhodchaad ke kalti maar lun, par phir unke sapnon ka kya? Dil itna bhari hai ki saans lena mushkil ho raha hai. Sab khush hain, sheher mein wahi bhaukaal hai, par mere andar ka sannata mujhe khaaye ja raha hai. Aaj khud ki nazron mein gir gayi hun yaar. Pura falooda ban gaya hai meri umeedon ka."
"Raat ke 3 baj rahe hain aur mere hostel ke kamre mein itna sannata hai ki mujhe apni hi dhadkan ki awaaz sunai de rahi hai. Sab so rahe hain, par meri aankhon mein neend ka naamonishan nahi hai. Jitni baar aankhein band karti hun, future ka wo dar ek horror movie ki tarah saamne aa jata hai. Dimaag mein sawalon ki bhagdad machi hui hai. Kya mujhe achhi job milegi? Kya main itni mehnat kar bhi rahi hun ki main baki sab ke bhaukaal competition mein tik saku? Mere saath wale log nayenaye certifications kar rahe hain, koi internship kar raha hai, aur mujhe lag raha hai ki main wahin ki wahin thami hui hun. Aisa lagta hai ki life ka pura falooda ban chuka hai. PapaMummy ki mujhse itni umeedein hain, unka har ek rupaya jo wo mujhpe kharch kar rahe hain, wo mere dimaag pe ek karz ki tarah chadh raha hai. Agar main fail ho gayi toh? Agar main unhe wo life nahi de paayi jiska unhone khwab dekha hai toh? Puri raat bas chhat ko ghoorte hue nikal gayi. Kabhi phone uthati hun toh LinkedIn pe logon ki success dekh ke aur siyappa lagne lagta hai. Sab aage nikal rahe hain aur main bas yahan baith ke apne darr se magajmari kar rahi hun. Subah hone ko hai, par mere andar ka andhera khatam nahi ho raha. Thakaan se sar phat raha hai, par ye future ka tension ek aise saamp ki tarah hai jo kaleje se lipta hua hai. Aaj pehli baar mehsoos ho raha hai ki bade hona kitna dardnak hota hai yaar. Sab kuch itna unstable lag raha hai ki rona bhi ab solution nahi lagta. Bas ek khaalipan hai jo andar hi andar khaaye ja raha hai."
"Yaar, aaj toh lag raha hai jaise kisi ne chaltechalte seene pe kantaap maar diya ho. Main bade maze mein Instagram scroll kar rahi thi, socha tha shayad uska koi post dikh jaye toh din chauchak ho jayega. Par jaise hi uski story kholi, wahan jo dekha usne meri duniya hi hila di. Wo kisi aur ladki ke saath tha. Dono kisi cafe mein baithe the aur wo ladki uske kandhe pe sar rakh ke has rahi thi. Caption mein likha thaThe One aur saath mein ek red heart. Bhai, us ek second mein mera pura dil satyanaash ho gaya. Wo ladki itni sundar lag rahi thi, uska makeup, uske baal... sab ekdum perfect. Usko dekh ke mujhe khud se nafrat hone lagi. Main yahan hostel mein bikhre baalon ke saath uski yaadon mein magajmari kar rahi hun, aur wo wahan apni nayi life ka bhaukaal jama raha hai. Aisa laga jaise saans atak gayi ho. Mere dimaag mein jo uske saath future ki matargasti chal rahi thi, uska ek jhatke mein falooda ban gaya. Maine turant Instagram band kiya aur phone bed pe fenk diya, par wo photo meri aankhon ke saamne se hat hi nahi rahi hai. Dost log group mein bakaiti kar rahe hain, par mere andar itna sannata chhaya hua hai ki kisi ko reply karne ki himmat nahi hai. Aisa lag raha hai ki main kabhi uske liye enough thi hi nahi. Ek tarfa pyaar ka ye siyappa aaj mujhe andar se khaali kar gaya. Raat ke andhere mein bas rona aa raha hai ki kyu maine itni umeed lagayi thi. Aaj toh dukh ka level next level hai yaar."
"Yaar, aaj canteen ka wo kona mujhe kaatne ko daud raha tha. Main pichle ek ghante se wahan baithi rahi, do baar chai mangwai, aur har baar darwaze ki taraf aise dekha jaise koi khoya hua khazana milne wala ho. Par koi nahi aaya. Group chat pe sabne Coming, 5 mins, aur Bas raste mein hun wali bakaiti peli thi, par ekek karke sabne kalti maar li. Kisi ka assignment pending ho gaya, toh kisi ko neend aa gayi. Asliyat toh ye hai ki shayad kisi ke liye meri presence itni matter hi nahi karti ki wo dhoop mein canteen tak aaye. Aaspaas dekha toh har table pe bhaukaal macha tha. Koi birthday celebrate kar raha tha, koi doston ke saath samoson pe toot pada tha, sabki apni ek duniya thi. Aur main? Main bas apne phone mein purane messages scroll karne ki acting kar rahi thi taaki canteen wale bhaiya ko ye na lage ki main yahan velli baithi hun. Izzat ka pura falooda ban raha tha wahan. Wo jo ek khaali kursi mere saamne thi na, wo mujhe meri aukat bata rahi thi. Aisa lag raha tha jaise bheed mein mera dam ghut raha ho. Maine socha tha thodi matargasti hogi, thoda dil halka hoga, par yahan toh aur zyada sannata dimaag mein bhar gaya. Jab mujhse aur nahi jhela gaya, toh maine apna bag uthaya aur wahan se nikal gayi. Raste bhar bas yahi lag raha tha ki hum jinhe apna sab kuch maante hain, unke liye hum bas ek option hote hain. Aaj canteen ki wo bench aur meri tanhai... dono ne milke mere mood ka satyanaash kar diya. Bahut rona aa raha hai apni is haalat pe."
"Yaar, aaj Papa ne jo sunaya hai na, usne mere andar tak ko jhinjhor ke rakh diya hai. Main toh bas doston ke saath thodi der ke liye bahr gayi thi ki dimaag ki magajmari kam ho jaye, par ghar lautte hi Papa ka chehra dekh ke samajh gaya ki aaj siyappa hone wala hai. Unhone bina kisi bhumika ke seedha bol diyaBas yahi sab bacha hai? Din bhar sirf ghumti rehti ho, kabhi kitabein bhi khol ke dekh liya karo ki padhai kab karogi? Paise kya ped pe ugte hain? Bhai, us waqt aisa laga jaise kisi ne mere muh pe thanda paani daal diya ho. Mere paas bolne ko bahut kuch thaki main kitni raat tak jag ke projects poore karti hun, ki kitna stress hai placements kapar unki aankhon mein wo gussa aur nirasha dekh ke meri zubaan pe sannata chha gaya. Wahan se toh main chupchap kalti maar ke apne kamre mein aa gayi, par unki wo baatein kaan mein hathaude ki tarah baj rahi hain. Unhe lagta hai meri life sirf matargasti hai, jabki andar se main har din apne future ko leke darr rahi hun. Maine socha tha wo meri mehnat ko samjhenge, par unke liye main bas ek careless ladki hun jo unka paisa barbaad kar rahi hai. Ab laptop saamne khula hai, code likhne ki koshish kar rahi hun, par ankhon ke saamne dhundhalapan"
"Yaar, aaj result dekhne ke baad se haathpair thande pad gaye hain. Maine socha tha thoda bahut toh manage ho hi jayega, par screen pe wo marks dekh kar dimaag ka pura falooda ban gaya. Itni mehnat, itni raaton ki magajmari, aur badle mein kya mila? Bas ye do digit ka number jo meri aukat bata raha hai. Ab hostel ke kone mein baithi hun aur phone ko aise ghoor rahi hun jaise wo koi bomb ho. Papa ka call aane hi wala hoga, unhone subah hi pucha tha, Beta, result ka kya hua? Unhe lagta hai unki beti sheher mein padh ke unka bhaukaal badhayegi, par unhe kya pata ki yahan mera pura confidence kalti maar chuka hai. Himat hi nahi ho rahi ki unhe sach bataun. Kaise bolun ki jiss padhai ke liye wo dinraat ek kar rahe hain, usme main itni buri tarah pichhad gayi hun? Jab wo sunenge, toh unke chehre pe wo jo sannata chayega na, wo mujhe andar tak maar dega. Mummy ki umeed bhari baatein yaad aa rahi hain, aur ab wo sab ek siyappa lag rahi hain. Dost log baahar party ki planning kar rahe hain, Arre marks toh aate rehte hain wali bakaiti pel rahe hain, par unhe nahi pata ki mere liye ye marks nahi, mere maabaap ka bharosa tha jo aaj toot gaya hai. Aisa lag raha hai jaise main unka gunehgar hun. Room ki light band karke baithi hun, par ye andhera darr se zyada sukoon de raha hai, kyunki kam se kam yahan kisi ko mera rota hua chehra toh nahi dikhega. Aaj sach mein lag raha hai ki sab khatam ho gaya."
"Yaar, ye subah ka alarm hai ya koi dushman ka bulawa? Roz raat ko main full bhaukaal mein 6 baje ka alarm lagati hun, ye soch kar ki kal toh pakka yoga karungi aur ekdum aesthetic subah bitaungi. Par jaise hi 6 baje wo phone cheekhna shuru karta hai, mera haath khudbakhud Snooze button pe chala jata hai. Pehla snooze, dusra snooze... bhai, maine poore 5 baar snooze dabaya! Har 5 minute mein mujhe lagta hai ki bas thodi der aur so jaun toh jannat mil jayegi. Dimaag mein ek taraf chalta hai ki late ho rahi hun, class chhoot jayegi, par neend ka nasha aisa hota hai ki sab kalti maar jata hai. 5th baar jab alarm baja, toh maine phone ko takiye ke niche dabane ki koshish ki, par tab tak dhoop mere chehre pe aane lagi thi. Wo jo aakhiri baar snooze dabake 2 minute ki neend aati hai na, wahi sabse khatarnak hai. Izzat ka toh wahi falooda ho jata hai jab dimaag ko pata chalta hai ki ab toh uthna hi padega. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par subah ki neend aur meri dushmani ekdum purani hai. Aaj bhi wahi hua, alarm thak gaya par meri neend nahi tuti!"
"Jab alarm fail ho jata hai, tab aata hai ghar ka sabse khatarnak weaponMummy ki awaaz! Aaj bhi wahi hua, jaise hi Mummy ne chillaya, Oye! 8 baj gaye hain, tiffin kya tere baap bharne aayenge?, meri saari neend wahi satyanaash ho gayi. Main hadbada ke aise uthi jaise room mein aag lag gayi ho. Mummy ki daant mein jo bhaukaal hota hai na, uske aage duniya ka koi alarm clock kaam nahi karta. Main aankhein malte huye kitchen pahunchi, jahan Mummy ne pehle hi garam chai bana rakhi thi. Bhai, wo pehli sip lete hi jo dimaag ka sannata khatam hua, wo main hi jaanti hun. Chai ki pyali pakdepakde maine Mummy ki wo subahsubah wali bakaiti suni ki kaise main dinbadin bigadti ja rahi hun. Par sach bataun, wo adrak wali chai aur Mummy ki daant ka combo hi hai jo mujhe asliyat mein jagata hai. Chai khatam kartekarte mujhe hosh aaya ki ab toh tayyar hone ke liye sirf 15 minute bache hain. Ek haath mein chai ka glass aur dusre mein towel, aaj subah ka scene ekdum siyappa wala tha par wo chai ekdum kantaap thi!"
"Chai peene ke baad jab main mirror ke saamne gayi, toh apni shakal dekh ke mera dimaag ekdum sannata maar gaya. Aisa lag raha tha jaise raati mein mere baalon ne koi kusti ladi hoaadhe baal hawa mein udd rahe the aur baaki ekdum bhasad machaye huye the. 22 saal ki umar mein ladkiyan subah mirror mein dekh ke good morning bolti hain, aur ek main hun jise lag raha tha ki mere sar pe kisi ne chidiya ka ghosla bana diya hai. Ab time toh tha nahi ki main shampoo karun ya dhang se styling karun, toh maine jaldijaldi tel lagaya aur comb se unhe thik karne ki magajmari shuru ki. Par wo baal bhi ekdum ziddi the, kalti maarne ka naam hi nahi le rahe the. Maine socha thoda spray daalun, par tab tak dhyan aaya ki college ki bus nikalne wali hogi. Aakhir mein thakhaar ke maine ek messy bun banaya, jo messy kam aur disaster zyada lag raha tha. Maine khud ko mirror mein dekh ke bola, Chalo, isey hi fashion bolke chala denge. Izzat ka falooda hone se bachane ke liye maine ek hair clip thoka aur bag uthake bhaagi. Aaj toh baalon ne meri sundarta ka pura satyanaash kar rakha tha!"
"Ghar se bahar nikli toh asli siyappa mera intezar kar raha tha. Maine badi style mein apni purani bike ki chabi lagayi, socha tha ekdum hero ki tarah nikalungi, par jaise hi self dabaya... karrkarrkarr! Bike ne toh jawab hi de diya. Ab shuru hui meri asli kashmakash. Maine stand lagaya aur kick maarna shuru kiya. Ek kick, do kick... bhai, poore 10 minute tak main wahan kusti ladti rahi. Mera face pasine se laal ho gaya aur mera naya kurta ganda hone laga. Pados wale Chacha balcony se dekh ke bakaiti kar rahe the, Bitiya, isey thoda dularo, tabhi chalegi. Maine man hi man unka satyanaash kiya aur poori takat laga ke aakhiri kick maari. Jab bike phutphut karke start hui, tab jaake meri saans mein saans aayi. Itni magajmari ke baad meri saari energy wahi khatam ho gayi thi. 22 saal ki ladki jab road pe bike pe kick maarti hai na, toh poora mohalla spectator ban jata hai. Izzat ka toh wahi falooda ho gaya tha, par shukr hai bike ne end time pe saath de diya varna aaj toh college ka rasta paidal hi tay karna padta. Pura din shuru hone se pehle hi main ekdum thak ke chur ho gayi thi!"
"Yaar, Banaras mein raho aur Lanka chowk pe traffic mein na phaso, aisa toh ho hi nahi sakta! Aaj main thoda late nikli thi aur dimaag mein pehle hi magajmari chal rahi thi ki Professor entry denge ya nahi. Jaise hi main Lanka pahunchi, wahan ka nazaara dekh ke mera dil sannata maar gaya. Chaaro taraf se autos, rickshaws aur bikes aise ghuse huye the jaise koi kusti ka maidan ho. Ek taraf se saand (bull) apni masti mein rasta roke khada tha aur dusri taraf se traffic police wale ka seeti bajatebajate bura haal tha. Main apni bike leke wahan ek inch bhi nahi hil paa rahi thi. Mere bagal mein ek rickshaw wala mere handle se apna pahiya bhida raha tha, maine use ghoor ke dekha toh wo apni hi bakaiti pelne laga. Itni garmi, upar se wo dhuaan aur logon ka hallameri saari fresh look ka wahi satyanaash ho gaya. Maine 15 minute tak wahan break aur accelerator ke saath kusti ladi. Mann toh kar raha tha bike yahin chhod ke kalti maar lun, par majboori thi. Jab 20 minute baad rasta khula, tab tak meri class shuru hoke 10 minute beet chuke the. Izzat ka pura falooda Banaras ki inhi sadkon pe roz hota hai, par aaj ka traffic toh ekdum kantaap level ka tha!"
"Lanka ka traffic paar karke jab main BHU ke Singh Dwar (gate) pahunchi, toh clock dekh ke meri saansein atak gayi. Main poore 25 minute late thi! Gate pe wahi khadoos wale guard uncle khade the jo bina ID card aur bina thikthak wajah ke kisi ko bakashte nahi hain. Maine apni bike ki speed kam ki aur ekdum masoom chehra banaya, jaise mujhse zyada shareef ladki poore Banaras mein nahi hai. Unhone haath deke roka aur pucha, Bitiya, itna late kyun? Abhi toh class khatam hone wali hogi. Maine bina sochesamjhe ek bhaukaal wala jhooth phek diya. Maine bola, Uncle, wo raste mein ek dadiamma gir gayi thin, unhe hospital pahunchane mein der ho gayi. Punyakarma kar rahi thi isliye thoda late ho gayi. Uncle ne thodi der mujhe sandeh se dekha, par mera masoom chehra dekh ke unka dil pighal gaya. Unhone bola, Chalo thik hai, par agli baar dhyan rakhna. Main man hi man hans rahi thi ki kaise maine unka falooda banaya, par jaise hi aage badhi, mujhe laga ki kahin upar wala sach mein mera satyanaash na kar de jhooth bolne ke liye. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par guard se bachne ke liye aaj bhi school bacchon wale bahane maarti hun. Khair, entry toh mil gayi par darr abhi bhi baaki tha!"
"Traffic aur guard ki magajmari ke beech jo ek cheez mujhe zinda rakhti hai, wo hai mera Playlist. Aaj jaise hi main gate se andar ghusi, maine apna favourite gaana Vibe Teri Meri Milti Hai lagaya. Bhai, jaise hi wo beat shuru hui, mera saara stress ekdum kalti maar gaya. Wo thandi hawa, BHU ki wo haribhari sadkein aur kaan mein bajta wo bassaisa lag raha tha jaise main kisi film ki heroine hun aur ye mera entry scene hai. Main bike chalatechalate dheredhere gunguna rahi thi, itna kho gayi thi ki mujhe pata hi nahi chala kab main apni department ki building cross kar gayi. Log raste mein dekh rahe the ki ye ladki itni khush kyun hai, par mujhe toh apna alag hi bhaukaal jamana tha. Gaane ne dimaag ka saara siyappa saaf kar diya tha. Wo jo 5 minute ka rasta hota hai na, wahi din ka sabse sukoon wala moment hota hai. Par maza tab kirkira hua jab gaana khatam hote hi mujhe Professor ki awaaz yaad aayi aur mera dimaag wapas se sannata maar gaya. Par jo bhi ho, wo gaana sun ke jo energy aayi, usne mera din ekdum chauchak bana diya tha!"
"Bhai, aaj kismat ne mere saath jo mazak kiya hai, wo main kabhi nahi bhoolungi. Subahsubah ki bhagdad aur bike ki magajmari mein, main wo tiffin bag uthana hi bhool gayi jise Mummy ne itni mehnat se Poha bhar ke rakha tha. Jab 2nd lecture mein mere pet mein chuhe kusti ladne lage, tab maine bag mein haath dala aur mujhe sirf khaali jagah mili. Mera dimaag wahi satyanaash ho gaya! Saamne Professor Machine Learning samjha rahe the aur mujhe har diagram mein sirf garamgaram samosa dikh raha tha. Mere bagal mein baithi Riya apna tiffin khol ke maze se paranthe tod rahi thi aur uski khushboo se meri halat aur falooda ho rahi thi. Maine dhere se pucha, Bhai, thoda de de?, par usne aisi look di jaise main uski jayedaad maang rahi hun. Poori class mein main bas ghadi ghurti rahi aur pet ki gurrgurr ko chhupane ki koshish karti rahi. Izzat ka pura kachra ho gaya jab lecture ke beech mein hi mere pet se zor ki awaaz aayi aur piche wale ladke hansne lage. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par bina khaye mera dimaag ek inch bhi nahi chalta. Aaj toh bhookh ne meri aisi tafri li ki ab canteen hi aakhiri sahara bacha hai. Pura din ekdum siyappa ho gaya!"
"Yaar, aaj ki subah Banaras ka mausam aisa tha ki mera mann hi nahi kiya ki main tayyar hoke college ki wahi purani magajmari mein jaun. Jaise hi maine balcony ka darwaza khola, thandi hawa ne ekdum se chehre ko chhua aur dimaag ka saara sannata khatam ho gaya. Halkihalki dhoop khili thi aur pedon pe chidiya aisi bakaiti kar rahi thin jaise wo bhi aaj bunk maarne ka plan bana rahi hon. Mujhe laga ki aaj ka din toh ekdum aesthetic hone wala hai. Maine jaldijaldi apni pasand ki kurti nikaali, thoda kajal lagaya aur ekdum chauchak hoke tayyar hui. Mausam itna pyaari tha ki maine socha aaj bike thoda dhere chalayungi taaki is vibe ko poora enjoy kar sakun. Jab raste mein BHU ki un haribhari sadkon se guzri, toh dil ekdum gardengarden ho gaya. Aisa lag raha tha jaise main kisi movie ki heroine hun jo kisi romantic gaane ki shooting pe ja rahi hai. Bhale hi college mein assignments ka siyappa intezar kar raha tha, par us suhaane mausam ne mera mood itna top level pe kar diya tha ki mujhe laga aaj toh main poori duniya jeet lungi. Kabhikabhi ye chotichoti khushiyan hi zindagi ka asli bhaukaal hoti hain!"
"Banaras mein raho aur raste mein paan na khao, ye toh waisa hi hai jaise bina namak ke khana. Aaj Lanka cross karte waqt mera mann hua ki thoda Banarasi andaaz dikhaya jaye. Maine ek purani, mashoor gumti (dukan) pe bike roki aur bade style se bola, Bhaiya, ek ekdum kantaap meetha paan lagana, ekdum gulkand aur saunf thok ke! Paan wale bhaiya ne bhi apne andaaz mein kathasupari ka bhaukaal dikhaya aur 2 minute mein laal rang ka ek mast paan mere haath mein thama diya. Jaise hi maine wo pehla nivala liya, bhai... aisa laga dimaag ki saari battiyan jal gayi hain. Wo thandak aur wo meethas, sach mein Banaras ki shaan hai. Main paan chabaate huye bike chala rahi thi aur man hi man soch rahi thi ki kitni chauchak dikh rahi hun. Par maza tab kirkira hua jab college gate pe meri ek senior mil gayi aur usne mujhse kuch pucha. Ab main paan thookun ya jawab dun? Maine dhere se hont dabaye aur bas sar hila ke kalti maar li. Izzat ka toh wahi falooda ho gaya tha, par wo paan ka swaad itna zabardast tha ki maine socha, Beizzati gayi tel lene, paan toh ekdum sahi tha! Aaj poora din mera muh laal raha aur doston ne jo bakaiti kari, wo alag hi siyappa tha."
"Bhai, aaj subah ka scene itna ganda tha ki main kya bataun. Meri roommate, Riya, ka dimaag pata nahi kahan rehta hai. Subah jab main late ho rahi thi aur bike ki chabi dhoond rahi thi, tab pata chala ki madam ne meri chabi apne handbag mein rakh li thi aur khud so rahi thi. Maine use jagaya toh wo mujhpe hi bhaukaal jhaadne lagi, Arre, galti se rakh li toh kya hua, itna kalesh kyun kar rahi hai? Bas phir kya tha, hum dono ke beech shuru ho gayi asli magajmari. Maine use sunaya ki kaise uski wajah se mera roz ka satyanaash hota hai, aur usne meri purani galtiyan gina di. Hamari ladai itni badh gayi ki paas wale room ki ladkiyan bhi darwaze se jhaankne lagin. Maine gusse mein apna bag uthaya aur use Bye tak nahi bola. Hostel se nikalte waqt mera mood ekdum falooda ho gaya tha. Poore raste main wahi baatein sochti rahi ki kaise wo mujhse itni bakaiti kar sakti hai. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par roommate ke saath wahi chhote bacchon wali ladai aaj bhi hoti hai. Aaj toh dimaag mein ek ajeeb sa sannata tha, par gussa usse bhi zyada tha. Lag raha hai aaj raat ko wapas jaake ek naya siyappa shuru hoga!"
"Sab kalesh aur magajmari ek taraf, par jab main BHU ke Singh Dwar se andar ghusi aur bike ki speed 40 pe pahunchayi, toh wo jo thandi hawa chehre pe lagi na... uff! Us ek pal ne mera saara gussa aur thakaan kalti maarne pe majboor kar diya. Banaras ki garmi ke baad jab subahsubah wo halki thandak feel hoti hai, toh aisa lagta hai dimaag ka sara stress wash ho gaya hai. Mere baal piche ud rahe the aur main ekdum heroine wali feeling le rahi thi. Main bike chalatechalate aadhi aankhein band karke us hawa ko enjoy kar rahi thi, itna kho gayi thi ki saamne se aate huye auto ko dekha hi nahi. Usne zor se horn bajaya toh mera bhaukaal wahi dher ho gaya aur main darr ke maare ladkhada gayi. Par phir bhi, wo jo sukoon hota hai na, bina kisi ki parwah kiye khuli sadak pe bike bhagaana, wahi asli freedom hai. 22 saal ki age mein jab aap khud bike chalake college jaate ho, toh wo selfconfidence ekdum chauchak hota hai. Aaj us thandi hawa ne mera din banaya tha, bhale hi roommate se ladai hui thi, par us moment mein sirf main thi aur meri bike ka ye mast siyappa!"
"Yaar, aaj kismat ne mere saath aisa siyappa kiya hai ki main kya bataun. Kal raat bhar Instagram pe reels dekhne ki matargasti mein, main phone charging pe lagana hi bhool gayi. Subah uthi toh dekha 15 battery hai, maine socha college pahunchtepahunchte kaam chal jayega. Par jaise hi 1st lecture shuru hua, mera phone Battery Low ka raag alapne laga. Bhai, us waqt jo mere dimaag mein sannata chhaya, wo main hi jaanti hun. 22 saal ki ladki ke liye bina phone ke college rehna matlab bin paani ki machhli jaisa hai. Mujhe notes lene the, doston ko message karke canteen bulana tha, par screen 2 pe aake atak gayi. Maine poori class mein idharudhar ghoora ki kahin koi charging point mil jaye, par meri kismat hi satyanaash thi main sabse piche wali bench pe baithi thi jahan switch board ka doordoor tak koi nishan nahi tha. Maine dhere se Riya se powerbank maanga, par usne aisi look di jaise maine uski kidney maang li ho. Jab phone Switch Off hua, toh aisa laga jaise mera poora connection duniya se kalti maar gaya. Izzat ka pura falooda tab hua jab Professor ne pucha, Notes kahan hain?, aur maine masoomiyat se bola, Sir, dimaag mein save kar rahi hun. Poora din bina phone ke aisa lag raha tha jaise main kisi purane zamane mein jee rahi hun."
"Bhai, aaj subahsubah ka bhaukaal Mummy ke call se shuru hua. Main abhiabhi hostel ke raste mein bike pe thi ki phone baja. Maine socha kuch important hoga, par jaise hi uthaya, udhar se Brahmastra chal gaya. Oye maharani! 9 baj gaye hain aur tu abhi raste mein hai? Raat bhar phone mein ghusi rahegi toh subah kahan se aankh khulegi? Mummy ki awaaz mein wo Banarasi teekhapan tha ki mujhe raste mein bike rokni padi. Maine dhere se bola, Mummy, wo raat mein assignment ki magajmari chal rahi thi, par Mummy toh Mummy hain. Unhone wahi puraana purana kachachittha khol diya ki kaise main sheher jaake bigad gayi hun aur ghar ki zimmedariyon se kalti maar rahi hun. Raste mein log rukruk ke dekh rahe the ki ye ladki helmet pehne daant kyun kha rahi hai. Izzat ka toh wahi falooda ho gaya beech sadak pe. Maine jaldijaldi Haanhaan mummy, thik hai bol ke phone kaata. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun, sheher mein akeli rehti hun, par Mummy ka wo Subah jaldi utho wala siyappa kabhi peecha nahi chhodta. Us daant ne meri neend toh bhaga di, par dimaag ka dahi zaroor kar diya!"
"Aaj meri bike ne subahsubah jawab de diya tha, toh mujhe Godowlia se rickshaw pakadna pada. Bhai, Godowlia ka jo bhasad hota hai na, wo kisi jung se kam nahi hai. Wahan rickshaw wale bhaiya se kiraye ki magajmari karna hi apne aap mein ek bada task hai. Maine ek bhaiya ko roka aur bola, BHU chalo ge?, unhone aisa rate bataya ki mera dimaag wahi satyanaash ho gaya. Maine Banarasi style mein bargaining shuru ki, Arre bhaiya, roz ka aanajaana hai, itna bhaukaal mat jamao! Aakhir mein baat bani aur main rickshaw pe baith gayi. Godowlia ki un patli galliyon se rickshaw nikalna ek alag hi adventure hai. Kabhi koi saand saamne aa raha hai toh kabhi koi tourist selfie le raha hai. Rickshaw wale bhaiya apni hi dhun mein HatoHato chilaye ja rahe the. Maine socha thoda cool dikhungi, par dhool aur dhuen ne mera naya makeup ekdum falooda kar diya. Rickshaw ki wo khadkhad mein mera sar ghumne laga. Jab 40 minute baad main college pahunchi, toh aisa lag raha tha jaise main koi kusti lad ke aayi hun. 22 saal ki age mein rickshaw ki ye ride ne mujhe ehsaas dila diya ki bike hi asli sukoon hai, rickshaw toh bas ek siyappa hai!"
"Subah ki itni magajmari aur rickshaw ki thakaan ke baad, jab maine Lanka ke paas ek purani chai ki tapri dekhi, toh mere kadam khudbakhud wahi ruk gaye. Wahan ka nazaara ekdum chauchak thamitti ke kulhad mein khaulti hui adrak wali chai aur uski wo mehek! Maine ek kulhad chai pakdi aur wahi bench pe baith gayi. Bhai, wo pehli sip lete hi aisa laga jaise meri saari thakaan kalti maar gayi ho. Tapri pe baithe log apniapni bakaiti pel rahe thekoi politics discuss kar raha tha toh koi college ki gossips. Maine bhi wahan baith ke thodi der sukoon ki saans li. Wo jo garam chai ka dhuaan aur Banaras ki subah wali vibe hoti hai na, wo dimaag ka saara sannata saaf kar deti hai. Maine chai ke saath ek maskabun bhi order kar diya kyunki bhookh se mera bura haal tha. Wahan baith ke mujhe ehsaas hua ki bhale hi kitna bhi siyappa ho jaye, ye ek kulhad chai sab thik kar deti hai. Jab main wahan se uthi, toh mera mood ekdum kantaap ho chuka tha. Ab main college ke kisi bhi lecture ka satyanaash jhelne ke liye taiyaar thi!"
"Yaar, Banaras ki subah aur Mummy ke haath ka garamgaram Pohaye combo ekdum chauchak hota hai! Aaj subah jab main nind mein magajmari kar rahi thi, tabhi kitchen se rai aur kadi patte ke tadke ki wo khushboo aayi ki meri saari neend wahi kalti maar gayi. Mummy ne ekdum Banarasi style mein poha banaya tha, jisme upar se dher saara sev, thodi kacchi pyaaz aur halka sa nimbu nichoda hua tha. Bhai, wo pehli chammach muh mein rakhte hi aisa laga jaise dimaag ka saara sannata khatam ho gaya ho. Maine full bhaukaal mein do plate poha pela, kyunki mujhe pata tha ki college mein toh phir wahi canteen ka falooda khana padega. Mummy piche se bol rahi thin, Dheere khao maharani, kahin bhaagi nahi ja rahi ho, par unhe kya pata ki unke haath ke swaad ke aage sab satyanaash hai. Wo nashta karke jo energy aayi, ussi ke dum pe main aaj poore din ki bakaiti jhelne ke liye taiyaar hui thi. Sach mein, dunya bhar ka burgerpizza ek taraf aur Mummy ka banaya wo poha ek taraf!"
"Aaj college jaate waqt maine apni best friend, Riya, ko raste mein pick karne ka plan banaya tha. Main uske ghar ke bahar pahunchi aur zorzor se horn bajana shuru kiya, itna halla machaya ki pados ke kutte bhi bakaiti karne lage. Jab wo bahar aayi, toh madam ekdum heropanti mein dhiredhire chal ke aa rahi thin. Maine chilaya, Oye, jaldi baith! Pehle hi traffic ne dimaag ka siyappa kar rakha hai! Wo piche baithi aur hamari bikepewaali gossip shuru ho gayi. Wo piche se mere kaan mein poore department ki gossips suna rahi thi aur main bike chalatechalate Hain? Sach mein? karke react kar rahi thi. Beechbeech mein jab main break maarti, toh wo mujhpe chillaati aur hum dono ki raste mein hi kusti shuru ho jati. Log dekh rahe the ki do ladkiyan bike pe itni matargasti kyun kar rahi hain, par humein apna alag hi bhaukaal jamana tha. Dosti mein yahi toh maza hai, rasta kitna bhi lamba ho, agar piche koi bakbak karne wala ho toh saari thakaan kalti maar jati hai. Aaj ki wo ride ekdum kantaap thi!"
"Bhai, aaj subah neend ne mere saath wo satyanaash kiya ki mera Beauty Routine hi dharashayi ho gaya. 5 baar snooze dabane ke chakkar mein mere paas tayyar hone ke liye sirf 10 minute bache the. Maine mirror mein dekha aur socha, Kajal lagau ya eyeliner?, par phir clock dekhi toh samajh aaya ki aaj sirf shakal dhona hi naseeb mein hai. Maine makeup ka dabba wahi patka aur bina kisi bhaukaal ke, ekdum natural look (jise log bhootlook bhi keh sakte hain) mein bahar nikal gayi. College pahunchi toh doston ne puchte hi mera falooda bana diya, Oye, aaj bimaar hai kya? Ya asli shakal dikhane ka mann ho gaya? Maine gusse mein unhe ghoora aur bola, Ye natural beauty hai, tum log nahi samjhoge! Par andar se mujhe pata tha ki bina kajal ke meri aankhein ekdum sannata lag rahi hain. Poore din main apne chehre ko dupatta se chhupane ki koshish karti rahi taaki koi highdefinition mein meri beizzati na kar de. Aaj pata chala ki 22 saal ki age mein NoMakeup Look carry karna kitna bada siyappa hai, khaas kar tab jab aap late uthe hon!"
"Yaar, aaj meri kismat ne aakhiri maut ka kuan tab dikhaya jab main class mein baithi aur Professor ne bola, Important notes hain, sab likhna shuru karo. Maine bade style se apna bag khola, haath andar dala, idharudhar tatola... par pen ka doordoor tak koi nishan nahi tha! Mera dimaag wahi satyanaash ho gaya. Maine socha shayad side pocket mein hoga, par wahan sirf purani bus tickets aur ek toffee ka wrapper nikla. Main 22 saal ki ho gayi hun, engineering ki student hun, par aaj bhi class mein bina pen ke baithi thiekdum falooda moment! Maine dhere se bagal wale ladke se pucha, Bhai, extra pen hai?, usne aisi shakal banayi jaise main usse uski jayedaad maang rahi hun. Phir maine Riya ko kohni maari, toh usne ek tuta hua pen diya jiska dhakkan bhi nahi tha. Poore lecture mein main us tute huye pen se kusti ladi aur apni kismat ki magajmari karti rahi. Izzat ka kachra tab hua jab Professor ne mera register dekha aur pucha, Ye pen hai ya chidiya ki tang? Aaj toh bhulakkadpan ne mera aisa siyappa karaya ki maine turant raste mein 5 pen ka set kharida!"
"Yaar, Banaras mein raho aur din ki shuruaat Baba ke darshan se na ho, toh lagta hai din mein kuch sannata reh gaya hai. Aaj main thoda jaldi uth gayi thi, toh maine socha BHU waale New VT (Vishwanath Temple) ho aati hun. Subahsubah wahan ki thandak aur dhoopbatti ki khushboo se dimaag ekdum chauchak ho jata hai. Main full speed mein gayi, chappal stand pe phenki aur line mein lag gayi. Mann mein chal raha tha, Baba, bas is baar internals nikalwa do, baaki main dekh lungi. Par bhai, darshan jaldi mein karna Banaras mein ek sapna hi hai. Wahan itni bheed thi ki meri saari planning ka satyanaash ho gaya. Maine jaldijaldi jal chadhaya, maathe pe chandan lagaya aur wahan se kalti maarne ki koshish ki, kyunki 9 baje ki class ka bhoot sar pe sawar tha. Mandir se nikalte waqt wo sukoon toh mila, par clock dekhi toh samajh aaya ki ab college pahunchne ke liye bike ko rocket banana padega. 22 saal ki umar mein bhagwan se rishta thoda give and take wala ho jata haimain prasad chadhati hun aur badle mein wo mera siyappa sambhal lete hain. Aaj ka din Baba ke bharose shuru toh hua, par bhagdad abhi baaki thi!"
"Bhai, Banaras ki sadkon pe asli boss hum log nahi, balki humari Gau Mata hoti hain. Aaj main VT se nikal ke full bhaukaal mein bike bhaga rahi thi, dimaag mein lecture chal raha tha aur haath accelerator pe tha. Tabhi achanak, ek ekdum hattikatti safed cow raste ke beech mein aake khadi ho gayi, jaise keh rahi ho, Beta, kahan ki jaldi hai? Pehle humein toh dekh lo. Maine itne zor se brake maara ki meri bike ka pichla pahiya hawa mein lehraye aur main girtegirte bachi. Mera dil dhakdhak karne laga aur dimaag mein ek dum sannata chha gaya. Maine unhe thoda hatane ki koshish ki, dhere se horn bajaya, par madam toh wahan aisi baithi thin jaise unka hi mahal ho. Piche se autos wale HatoHato chilake alag hi bhasad macha rahe the. Izzat ka pura falooda tab hua jab wo cow meri taraf dekh ke aisi moo kari jaise meri beizzati kar rahi ho. Maine 5 minute wahan intezar kiya aur aakhir mein ek patli si gali se kalti maari. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par aaj bhi in sadkon pe cow se darr lagta hai. Pura mood wahi satyanaash ho gaya, par chalo, kam se kam hadsa hone se bach gaya!"
"Subah ki bhagdad aur raste ke kalesh ke baad, mera ek hi sahara hota haimera earphone. Maine raste mein Apna Bana Le lagaya aur bike ki speed thodi set ki. Bhai, wo gaana aur Banaras ki subah wali thandi hawa, aisa lagta hai jaise zindagi mein koi dukh hi nahi hai. Main gaane mein itna kho gayi thi ki mujhe pata hi nahi chala kab main Lanka cross kar gayi aur kab department ki building samne aa gayi. Main bike chalatechalate dhere se gunguna rahi thi, tabhi ek red light pe maine dekha ki bagal wala ladka mujhe ajeeb nazron se dekh raha hai. Shayad main thoda zyada zor se Piyaaaaa chilla di thi! Izzat ka wahi falooda ho gaya. Maine turant nazrein churayi aur helmet ke andar apna muh chhupane ki koshish ki. Par sach bataun, wo gaane hi hain jo mujhe college pahunchne tak ka hosla dete hain, varna Professor ki shakal yaad aate hi dimaag mein siyappa shuru ho jata hai. Jab tak main parking mein pahunchi, mera mood ekdum kantaap ho chuka tha. Gaane ne saari negativity kalti karwa di thi aur main class ke liye ekdum ready thi!"
"Yaar, aaj subah neend ka nasha aisa tha ki maine nashte ka pura satyanaash kar diya. Alarm snooze karne ke chakkar mein mere paas sirf itna time tha ki main kapde pehnu aur bhagun. Mummy kitchen se chilla rahi thin, Oye, khali pet jayegi toh dimaag ki batti kaise jalegi?, par maine suniansuni karke wahan se kalti maar li. Dimaag mein ek hi plan thacanteen ka garam samosa aur chai! Raste mein bike chalate waqt mere pet mein aisi magajmari chal rahi thi ki mujhe har red light pe samosa hi dikh raha tha. 22 saal ki age mein bhookh bardasht karna sabse bada task hai. Jab main college pahunchi aur 1st lecture mein baithi, toh mera dimaag padhai mein kam aur canteen ke menu mein zyada tha. Professor Database Management samjha rahe the aur mujhe lag raha tha ki Query se zyada zaroori Kachori hai. Izzat ka kachra tab hua jab meri dost ne pucha, Aaj itni khamosh kyun hai?, aur maine dhere se bola, Bhai, energy save kar rahi hun canteen tak jaane ke liye. Aaj toh bhookh ne mera pura siyappa kar rakha tha, bas intezar tha ki kab ye lecture khatam ho aur main foodcounter pe bhaukaal machaun!"
"Bhai, aaj subah jab Mummy ne kitchen se khushkhabri di ki aaj tiffin mein Aloo Paratha hai, toh meri saari thakaan wahi kalti maar gayi. Banarasi Mummy ke haath ka aloo paratha matlabdher saara makkhan, masaledar aloo ki stuffing aur saath mein wo teekhi hari chutney. Maine jaldijaldi tiffin pack kiya aur man hi man khush ho rahi thi ki aaj toh lunch break mein mera hi bhaukaal hoga. College pahunchte hi maine doston ko ishaara kar diya ki Aaj koi canteen nahi jayega, meri tiffin khulegi! Jaise hi break hua, hum sab ek bench pe dhera jama ke baith gaye. Maine jaise hi tiffin khola, uski mehek se poore corridor mein bhasad mach gayi. Mere dost aise tute paranthon pe jaise sadiyon se bhookhe hon. Maine ek byte li hi thi ki Riya ne pura parantha chheen liya! Izzat ka pura falooda tab hua jab Professor ne pucha, Ye canteen ki khushboo class mein kahan se aa rahi hai? Maine turant tiffin band kiya aur aise baith gayi jaise main kuch jaanti hi nahi. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par Mummy ke paranthon ke liye aaj bhi doston se kusti ladti hun. Aaj toh pet aur mann dono ekdum kantaap ho gaye!"
"Yaar, aaj subah kismat ne mere saath ek naya siyappa kiya. Main full speed mein college ke liye nikli thi, dimaag mein lecture chal raha tha, tabhi achanak meri bike ghutghut karne lagi. Maine meter dekha toh meri saansein atak gayifuel ka kanta ekdum E pe aake so gaya tha! Maine socha shayad thoda aur chal jaye, par bike ne raste ke beech mein hi dum tod diya. Izzat ka pura falooda ho gaya jab mujhe apni bike paidal dhakelte huye petrol pump tak le jaani padi. Log aise dekh rahe the jaise main koi naya experiment kar rahi hun. Petrol pump pe pahunchi toh wahan bhi lambi line ki magajmari! Garmi mein khadekhade mera pura makeup satyanaash ho gaya. Jab meri baari aayi, maine bola, Bhaiya, full kar do, aaj risk nahi lena! Petrol dalwane ke baad jab bike start hui, tab jaake dimaag ka sannata khatam hua. 22 saal ki age mein ye reserve pe bike chalane ki aadat mujhe kisi din bada dhoka degi. Aaj toh late hone ka pura bhaukaal set ho chuka tha, bas petrol ne rula diya!"
"Aaj subah jab main tayyar hoke mirror ke saamne khadi hui, toh pata nahi kyun, ek alag hi good vibe feel ho rahi thi. Maine apne baal sahi kiye, halka sa kajal lagaya aur khud ko dekh ke ek badi si smile pass ki. Kabhikabhi hota hai na, jab aapko lagta hai ki aaj sab kuch ekdum chauchak hone wala hai. Mirror mein dekh ke maine khud se bola, Beta, aaj toh tu phod degi! Wo ek chhoti si smile ne mere dimaag ka saara siyappa saaf kar diya tha. Main room se nikli toh mera confidence ekdum top level pe tha. Raste mein jab bhi koi red light aati, main side mirror mein apni shakal dekh ke thoda pout bana rahi thi. Log shayad soch rahe honge ki ye ladki subahsubah itni khush kyun hai, par mujhe toh apni Main Character wali feeling enjoy karni thi. 22 saal ki age mein jab aap khud se pyaar karna seekhte ho, toh din apne aap kantaap nikalta hai. Aaj us ek smile ne mere poore din ka bhaukaal set kar diya tha, bhale hi aage kitni bhi magajmari kyun na ho!"
"Bhai, hostel se nikalna kisi spy movie ke mission se kam nahi hai, khaas kar tab jab aapki Warden Maam gate pe hi darbaar lagaye baithi hon. Aaj subah main thoda late thi aur mujhe pata tha ki agar unhone pakad liya, toh 15 minute tak discipline pe lecture sunna padega aur mera pura din satyanaash ho jayega. Maine dhere se apna bag uthaya, dabe paon corridor se nikalne ki koshish ki. Jaise hi gate paas aaya, maine dekha Maam kisi doosri ladki ko daant rahi thin. Maine wahi mauka dekha aur apni bike ki chabi mutthi mein dabayi taaki awaaz na ho. Main deewar ke saharesahare aise kalti maari jaise main koi prothief hun. Jab gate ke bahar pahunchi aur bike start ki, tab jaake dil ka sannata khatam hua. Wo jo escape karne ka thrill hota hai na, uska alag hi bhaukaal hai! 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par Warden se aaj bhi waisa hi darr lagta hai jaise 1st year mein lagta tha. Aaj ka mission successful raha aur main bina kisi siyappa ke college ke liye nikal gayi!"
"Yaar, Banaras ke auto wale aur unka heavy driver wala attitudebhai, ye ek alag hi dukh hai. Aaj main Lanka ke paas apni bike ekdum sahi lane mein chala rahi thi, tabhi achanak ek auto wale ne bina signal diye, bina piche dekhe, mere ekdum saamne cut maar diya. Maine itne zor se brake maara ki meri bike ka pichla pahiya charrrrr karke phisla. Mera gussa ekdum chauchak level pe pahunch gaya! Maine bike side mein lagayi aur usse pucha, Bhaiya, aankh band karke chala rahe ho kya? Usne ulta mujhpe hi bhaukaal jhaadna shuru kar diya, bola, Arre bitiya, rasta toh khali tha! Maine bhi Banarasi style mein sunaya, Khali rasta hai toh kya mere upar chada doge? Izzat se chala lo varna abhi traffic police ko bulati hun. Poore 5 minute tak wahan magajmari chalti rahi, log ruk ke dekh rahe the aur mera dimaag ekdum sannata maar gaya tha. Izzat ka pura falooda ho gaya beech sadak pe jab usne dhere se bola, Madam, thoda dheere chillao, poora Banaras sun raha hai. Maine gusse mein wahan se kalti maari, par us auto wale ne mera pura subah ka mood satyanaash kar diya tha!"
"Aaj subah jab main BHU ki sadkon se guzar rahi thi, toh aasman ka rang aisa tha ki mera dimaag ekdum gardengarden ho gaya. Halkihalki narangi aur gulaabi dhoop badalon ke beech se aisi jhaank rahi thi jaise koi Pinterest wali photo ho. Maine socha itna chauchak view hai, ek story toh banti hai! Maine bike roki, phone nikala aur ek mast slowmo video banaya jisme pedon ki chhaon aur wo pyara sky dikh raha tha. Maine piche Pasoori ka ek remix lagaya aur likha Morning Bliss (bhale hi mera dimaag siyappa mein tha). Story daalte hi mere doston ke replies aane lage, Oye topper, college ja rahi hai ya photoshoot pe? Maine unhe ignore kiya aur apna bhaukaal maintain rakha. 22 saal ki age mein jab tak aapki life ki har chhoti khushi Instagram pe na jaye, tab tak sukoon nahi milta. Bhale hi uske 5 minute baad hi main traffic mein phasi thi, par un 30 seconds ki story ne mujhe poore college mein Aesthetic Queen wali feeling de di thi. Aaj ka mood ekdum kantaap set ho gaya tha!"
"Bhai, aaj kismat ne mujhe aise bachaya jaise kisi film ki heroine ko hero bachata hai. Main Lanka chowk ke paas thi aur maine dhyan nahi diya ki aage checking chal rahi hai. Mere paas helmet toh tha, par main jaldi mein apna physical DL (Driving License) ghar hi chhod aayi thi. Jaise hi maine door se safed wardi dekhi, mere dimaag mein maut ka sannata chha gaya. Mujhe laga aaj toh 20003000 ka phatka pakka hai aur Papa se jo daant padegi uska toh satyanaash hi samajho! Maine turant dimaag lagaya aur ek patli si gali mein bike ghusa di. Maine mirrors mein dekha ki koi piche toh nahi aa raha, aur wahan 2 minute tak aise chhupi rahi jaise main koi undercover agent hun. Jab rasta saaf dikha, toh maine dusre lambe raste se kalti maari. Dil dhakdhak kar raha tha aur haath kaamp rahe the, par wo jo bach nikalne wali khushi thi na, uska alag hi bhaukaal tha. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par aaj bhi traffic police ko dekh ke wahi chorsipahi wali feeling aati hai. Aaj toh Izzat ka falooda hotehote bacha, par adrenaline rush ekdum chauchak mil gaya!"
"College pahunch ke jab maine apna bag bench pe rakha aur phone check kiya, toh sabse upar Mummy ka WhatsApp message thaek pyari si phoolon wali photo aur niche likha tha, Shubh Prabhat bitiya, time pe khana kha lena aur dhyan se bike chalana. Bhai, wo message dekh ke mera saara gussa aur subah ka siyappa ek second mein khatam ho gaya. Mummy bhale hi subah daant ke bhaga dein, par unka ye wala pyaar ekdum kantaap hota hai. Maine dhere se muskura ke Love you Mummy reply kiya. Piche se doston ne dekh liya aur shuru ho gayi unki bakaiti, Oye, mummy ki ladli, abhi se ghar ki yaad aane lagi? Maine unhe ghoora aur bola, Tum log nahi samjhoge, ye emotional support hai! Sach bataun, din bhar ki itni magajmari aur assignments ke dukh ke beech, Mummy ka wo ek chhota sa message dimaag ka sara satyanaash thik kar deta hai. 22 saal ki age mein bhi jab aapko koi itna fikar karne wala hota hai, toh lagta hai duniya mein sab sahi hai. Aaj Mummy ke us message ne mera din sach mein Good Morning bana diya tha!"
"Yaar, Banaras mein rehne ka sabse bada bhaukaal ye hai ki yahan ki subah mein ek alag hi ruhaniyat hoti hai. Aaj subah jaise hi meri aankh khuli, maine sabse pehle apna phone uthaya aur wahi purani photo dekhi jo maine pichle hafte Dashashwamedh Ghat ki aarti ke waqt khichi thi. Subahsubah Ganga Ji ki wo shant lehrein aur ugta hua suraj dekh ke dimaag ka saara sannata ek second mein khatam ho jata hai. Aisa lagta hai jaise Baba Vishwanath khud bol rahe hon, Bitiya, aaj ka din ekdum chauchak jayega. Bhale hi main hostel ke kamre mein thi, par wo ek photo dekh ke aisa laga jaise main ghat ki thandi seedhiyon pe baithi hun. 22 saal ki age mein jab sheher ka shor aur padhai ki magajmari dimaag garam kar deti hai, tab ye ek photo hi sukoon ka kaam karti hai. Maine wahi photo apni Insta story pe lagayi aur likha Sukoon, bhale hi mujhe pata tha ki 10 minute baad college ke liye bhagdaud machne wali hai. Wo moment meri subah ka sabse haseen hissa tha, jisne mere din ka bhaukaal set kar diya!"
"Bhai, raste mein bike chalate waqt jab phone bajta hai na, toh dimaag mein pehle hi siyappa shuru ho jata hai. Aaj main Lanka cross kar rahi thi ki Riya ka call aaya. Maine socha shayad koi important class update hogi, par madam toh full bakaiti ke mood mein thi. Oye! Tune suna? Hamare department ki wo Miss Perfect ka kiske saath panga ho gaya? Bas phir kya tha, maine ek hath se helmet sambhala aur raste ke kinare bike roki. Poore 10 minute tak wahan sadak kinare khade hoke hamari gossip ki magajmari chalti rahi. Usne poora kachachittha khol diya aur main bas Hain? Sach mein? Kab hua? karti rahi. Izzat ka pura falooda tab hua jab piche se ek uncle ne zor se horn bajaya aur bola, Bitiya, ghar pe baith ke panchayat kar lo, rasta kyun roka hai? Maine hadbada ke phone rakha aur wahan se kalti maari. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par doston ki gossip ke liye class late kar dena mera purana pesha hai. Aaj subah ka wo gossip session itna masaledar tha ki meri saari thakaan wahi khatam ho gayi!"
"Aaj subah neend ne mere saath wo satyanaash kiya ki nashte ka pura plan hi dharashayi ho gaya. Jab aankh khuli toh 830 baj rahe the aur 9 baje meri lab class thi. Mummy kitchen se chilla rahi thin, Nashta kar le!, par mere paas baith ke pohaparatha khane ka time kahan tha? Maine dekha fridge mein kal ki Idli rakhi thi, maine bina garam kiye do idli uthayi, chutney mein duboyi aur khadekhade hi pel li. Bhai, wo thandi idli gale mein aise phasi ki mujhe lag raha tha aaj toh mera falooda pakka hai. Maine jaldijaldi paani piya, bag uthaya aur wahan se aisi kalti maari ki kya bataun. 22 saal ki engineering student ki life mein sitdown breakfast ek luxury ban gayi hai. Raste mein bike chalate waqt mera dimaag bas wahi idli digest karne mein laga tha. Izzat ka kachra tab hua jab class mein mere pet se ajeeb si awaaz aayi aur doston ne pucha, Aaj subah kya khaa ke aayi hai? Maine bas sar jhuukaya aur chupchaap baith gayi. Aaj toh jaldbazi ne nashte ka swaad aur meri dignity, dono ka siyappa kar diya!"
"Yaar, aaj mere bhulakkadpan ne mera wo satyanaash karaya ki main rone wali ho gayi thi. Main hostel se nikli, bike start ki aur gate tak pahunch gayi, dimaag mein full bhaukaal tha ki aaj toh time pe pahunchungi. Tabhi achanak thandi hawa mere baalon se takrayi aur mujhe ehsaas hua kiArre! Mera helmet kahan hai? Maine sar pe hath lagaya toh wahan sirf khali maidan tha! Mera dimaag wahi sannata maar gaya. Ab gate se wapas room tak jana matlab pura 10 minute ka extra siyappa. Maine gusse mein bike ghumaai aur wapas parking mein lagayi. Warden Maam gate pe khadi hoke muskura rahi thin, jaise keh rahi hon, Ho gaya na falooda? Main bhaagte huye room mein gayi, helmet uthaya aur wapas aayi. Is chakkar mein mera poora mood kharab ho gaya aur main class ke liye officially late ho gayi. 22 saal ki age mein itni chhoti baat bhool jana sach mein dimaag ka dahi kar deta hai. Aaj toh us ek helmet ne mera poora morning schedule kalti karwa diya!"
"Yaar, aaj subah jab main uthi toh pata nahi kyun mera mood ekdum satyanaash ho rakha tha. Na toh taiyaar hone ka mann tha aur na hi kisi se bakaiti karne ka. Dimaag mein bas wahi purane assignments aur aane wale exams ka sannata chhaya hua tha. Maine socha agar isi mood mein college gayi toh pakka kisi se jhagda karke apna falooda karwa lungi. Maine apni bike nikaali aur jaise hi earphones mein Udaan wala gaana bajaya, bhai... dimaag ki saari negativity kalti maar gayi! Wo bass aur wo lyrics sunte hi mere andar ka bhaukaal wapas aa gaya. Main raste mein dheredhere gunguna rahi thi aur hawa mein haath lehraye toh side wale uncle ne mujhe aise dekha jaise main paagal ho gayi hun. Par mujhe kya parwah? 22 saal ki age mein music hi hamara asli mood changer hota hai. Department pahunchtepahunchte main itni khush thi ki maine khadoos guard uncle ko bhi Good Morning bol diya. Aaj toh ek gaane ne mera poora din chauchak bana diya!"
"Bhai, thand ka mausam ho aur Banaras ki galliyon mein Malaiyyo na dikhe, aisa ho hi nahi sakta! Aaj main Lanka se guzri toh ek dukan pe wo kesar wala peela jhaag (Malaiyyo) dher saara mitti ke kulhad mein saja dekha. Upar se pista aur badam ki aisi barish ho rakhi thi ki mera dimaag wahi satyanaash ho gaya. Mann toh kiya ki bike wahin patku aur doteen kulhad pel lun. Par clock dekhi toh samajh aaya ki agar yahan ruki toh Professor meri class ka falooda bana denge. Maine bade bhari mann se accelerator ghumaya aur wahan se nikli, par dimaag mein abhi bhi wahi mithaas aur thandak ghum rahi thi. Poore raste main bas yahi soch rahi thi ki kab ye classes khatam hon aur main wapas aake is pe toot padun. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun par Banaras ke swaad ke aage mera selfcontrol hamesha kalti maar jata hai. Aaj toh bas lalach mein hi poora rasta nikal gaya, par wo khushboo abhi bhi dimaag mein bhaukaal macha rahi thi!"
"Yaar, college pahunchna ek jung hai toh bike park karna usse bhi badi magajmari! Aaj main jaise hi parking area mein ghusi, dekha ki wahan toh pehle se hi Kumbh ka mela laga hua hai. Har kisi ne apni bike aisi tedimedi lagayi thi ki ek inch bhi jagah nahi bachi thi. Maine socha piche wali row mein lagau, par wahan seniors ne apna alag hi bhaukaal jama rakha tha. Main 10 minute tak apni bike aagepiche karti rahi, mera chehra pasine se laal ho gaya aur mera naya scarf handle mein phas ke satyanaash ho gaya. Izzat ka pura falooda tab hua jab main ek bike hata rahi thi aur mere pairo ke niche se sandle phisal gayi. Piche se ladke hasne lage aur maine gusse mein unhe aisa ghoora ki sab sannata maar gaye. Aakhir mein ek kone mein dhabbe jaisi jagah mili jahan maine apni bike thons di. Is parking ke chakkar mein main class mein 5 minute aur late ho gayi. 22 saal ki engineering student hun par ye parking ka siyappa mujhe aaj bhi hara deta hai!"
"Sab siyappa aur kalesh ek taraf, par Mummy ka wo pyaar ek taraf. Aaj main late ho rahi thi aur dimaag ekdum garam tha, par Mummy ne bola, Bitiya, do minute baith, parantha garam kar diya hai, kha ke ja. Unhone ekdum kurchan wala karara parantha mere saamne rakha aur saath mein wo ghar ka bana aam ka achaar. Bhai, wo pehli byte lete hi mera saara gussa wahi kalti maar gaya. Unka wo nashta garam karke dena sirf khana nahi, balki mere liye poore din ka fuel hota hai. Maine jaldijaldi khaya, Mummy ke pair chhuye aur unhone dhere se bola, Dhyan se chalana. Us waqt jo dil mein sukoon mila na, usse mera din apne aap chauchak ho gaya. Bhale hi raste mein traffic mile ya Professor daantein, par Mummy ka wo garam nashta dimaag mein ek alag hi bhaukaal bhar deta hai. 22 saal ki ho gayi hun, sheher mein hostel mein rehti hun, par ghar ka wo swaad hi hai jo mujhe har mushkil se ladne ki takat deta hai. Aaj ka din Mummy ke naam!"
